description:
About Coultons Melbourne

Our clients prefer the individual and personal continuing service of knowing that we are 'their family agent'. We not only focus on the current transaction, but look after our clients over the years with all of their property needs. Your immediate requirement may be to sell a family home. Later there may be a need to buy an investment property to lease out either personally or through a super fund, change business premises or be the executor of an estate. We can help with any of these objectives.

Our confidential advice takes into account all of your property needs and personal concerns. It is important to thoroughly make sure that your property decisions are based on sound principals before you act.

We can assist and advise on investment properties, matrimonial disputes and partnership dissolutions, deceased estates and mortgagee's sales, commercial, industrial and business transactions.

Our service extends throughout the northern and eastern suburbs of Melbourne. With modern communications, mobile phones and the internet the 'local agent' syndrome went out years ago, so we are able to assist with your needs in any north-eastern, northern or eastern suburb. However, only qualified, experienced and competent estate agents can successfully achieve results consistently. We offer far more than just being a local agent.

Between 80-90% of our work is by way of either recommendation or referral. We always welcome new customers, so please give us a call if you are looking for a reliable service. Remember there is no substitute for quality service.

Independence

We are proudly an Australian owned independent office.

Most multi office groups rely on massive marketing (at your cost) and the 'glossy tag' of a network or franchise brand name. Therefore making their size a ‘perception’ only. Their 'one size fits all' formula is not suitable for many property owners.      

Smaller independent agencies can outperform most larger multi offices due to their more personal level of service, expertise and attention to detail.

COULTONS MELBOURNE is headed by Graham Coulton A.R.E.I  C.E.A. (R.E.I.V.) who supervises all the day to day activity of the business.

Graham started his career in 1972 and has worked in all roles within the industry. Graham is an individual member of the Real Estate Institute of Victoria.

Office                                                                                        

Our corporate office is centrally located in Ivanhoe on Melbourne's 8k radius, which positions us perfectly to service the northern; north eastern; eastern suburbs and the inner suburbs towards the CBD.
name: Coultons Melbourne

description: Since the establishment of the firm by W.G. Miles in 1924, the company has grown to a staff of 65, with nearly 3000 properties under management. Our firm's position as a market leader is testament to the fact that we take great pride in our reputation as one of Melbourne's most reputable and active Real Estate Agents. Our strong links with the community for 80 years have enabled us to build an intimate and practical understanding of the real estate market. Together with an established, prominent presence, years of successful experience and vast knowledge, we offer a service unrivalled by our competitors.

description:
Since 1971 Nelson Alexander has stood for the highest possible levels of professional conduct as the only means to achieve consistently outstanding results.

We are not a franchise - we are one single team spread out over sixteen offices. Each of these are managed by senior partners and by working together to share ideas and knowledge we deliver the most comprehensive, dynamic and compelling real estate service in Melbourne's north.

We believe that our high-quality service is driven by a commitment to being trustworthy, transparent, and always having a serious and genuine regard for “doing the right thing”. Keeping our promises and acting with integrity are obligations we hold steadfast for our staff.

Our core values are based on unity and teamwork, and our unique structure allows us to work together to share ideas, knowledge and experience in order to deliver exceptional results.

Our connection with our local communities runs deep within our company’s culture, and we are proactive in delivering meaningful responses to the needs of worthwhile causes through the Nelson Alexander Charitable Foundation.

Nelson Alexander is truly the largest real estate agency in Melbourne’s northern suburbs. The sheer volume of transactions we conduct gives us vital insight and knowledge of what’s happening in the marketplace and therefore the ability to provide the most reliable and accurate advice for your next real estate transaction.

“Large Residential Agency of the Year 2020 (REIV)”
name: Nelson Alexander Ivanhoe

Selling a property can be a very emotional and stressful time. It is a huge decision for most of us whether it is our own personal home or an investment property.

Love Real Estate has been successfully selling and leasing property in your area since 1945.

description: OUR MISSION: To be the real estate agency of choice in Melbourne's Northern suburbs due to our can do attitude and by providing service beyond the expectations of our customers and clients as our minimum standard. Lauders Real Estate has a grand history. Operating in the Diamond Valley since 1976, originally as Nicholas Lauder. There has been an enormous amount of change during the past 28 years. Not the least being the level of service requested from the community in general. We pride ourselves on always being ahead of the service level expected from our clients. Our privately owned network, firmly established in the area, has a proven history of success that has been built on a tradition of service, value and performance. Every Department at Lauders combines a history of client satisfaction with a culture that embraces ethics in Real Estate. Our goal is to be the agent of choice for all potential home sellers, buyers, landlords and tenants in the Diamond Valley due to our commitment to our clients and our passion to provide the best. Lauders has several company directors, each committed to our mission. It is a company that embraces technology, keeps abreast of industry updates and changing legislation whilst recognising the importance of constantly moving forward to stay ahead of its competitors. The services provided at Lauders Real Estate include: Residential Property Sales Commercial Property Sales Land Development Land Estate, Sales and Marketing Property Management House & Land Packages Project Development Financial Services to clients through Abcorp Financial Services Each of these services make up departments within Lauders, which each consist of a team of dedicated staff working solely in their area of expertise.

description:
Selling your business doesn't have to be hard. We are leading business brokers doing things the right way. 

What's our point of difference you ask? We do things right, and offer the highest security for our clients. We utilise trust accounting for all funds received so you know where your investment is going. We use contracts prepared by the best solicitors in Melbourne to ensure sales go through without drama or disruption to your business. We employ the strictest level of confidence for all our vendors & purchasers and assist in all aspects of the sale to ensure a smooth transition from vendor to purchaser.

Check out our website, read our blogs and our testimonials and learn what we can do for you today.

We are Melbourne-based and Victorian specialists, at Absolute good is never good enough. We are at the forefront of the industry - in knowledge, innovation, technology, and in pioneering new services.
Our mission is to remain at the forefront of business sales and to stay one step ahead with technology and the latest innovations.

Our clients are our lives, and their businesses are our lives. By maintaining the utmost ethical standards and understanding the emotional processes, our purpose is not only to achieve maximum results, but follow through to ensure a smooth transition for all parties involved.

Don't be fooled by agents claiming extraordinarily high success rates and databases of potential purchasers, the market is difficult as the economy fluctuates.

We will give you an honest evaluation based on our knowledge & experience, and we will help prepare your business for the best chance at a successful sale. We can recommend accountants & solicitors highly experienced in business sales, as well as assist buyers in organising finance.
name: Absolute Business Brokers

Welcome to Ray Mascaro & Co. Pty Ltd Real Estate Service with Excellence Buying or Selling, Real Estate decisions are possibly the most important you will ever make.

Selecting the right agent to assist in this major transaction is therefore of vital importance. The office was established in 1968 by A. R. Butler since then the Company has continued to offer a Professional Real Estate Service. Our slogan now is "Real Estate Service With Excellence." This is our objective. Since 1971 under the Directorship of Mr. Ray Mascaro, the company has grown to be one of the industries leaders in the Northern Suburbs, specialising in all facets of residential and commercial real estate from sales and marketing to property management and investment. Why List With Us?

1. TOTAL COMMITMENT Because you put your confidence in us, we will provide you with the best professional assistance needed. We have proven commitment, honesty and dedication to our clients that will enable us to help make your real estate experience an enjoyable one.

2. KNOWLEDGE AND EXPERTISE All our staff are fully trained to the area, services and facilities. We have the expertise, education and training to professionally represent you in all your real estate needs.

3. PROFESSIONAL MARKETING PLAN AIn order to achieve the highest price, you need to market your home professionally. We can design an individual Marketing Plan to best suit your property. We offer all our advertising in "Full color print", including all our brochures in color. We will expose your property through 3 internet sites to better expose your property: realestate.com.au, realestateview.com.au and our own www.raymascaro.com.au

4. REGULAR FEEDBACK We will ensure that you are kept informed regularly on the progress and the interest created for your property.

5. SERVICE WITH EXCELLENCE The office was established in 1968 by A. R. Butler since then the Company has continued to offer a Professional Real Estate Service. Our slogan now is Real Estate Service With Excellence. This is our objectives.

6. SECURITY We will always inform you prior to any inspections carried out and any open for inspections that may be scheduled.

7. CONFIDENTIALITY When you engage us to act as your agent, we honor your privacy and keep all business dealings strictly confidential.

8. KNOW WHO YOU ARE DEALING WITH All negotiations will be handled through our office. You will be dealing with knowledgeable, responsible and experienced people who are authorized to act on your behalf.

description:
Love Commercial represents the natural expansion of the family run Love Real Estate residential network founded in 1945 by Mr E J Love.

The original office of Love Real Estate was established in the newly created Melbourne suburb of Reservoir, and with the rapid growth since then of Melbourne City to the North, Love Real Estate now has an additional 6 offices located in Thornbury, Preston, Thomastown, Mill Park and Epping.

With the further construction of Melbourne’s Western Ring Road and CityLink, and the resulting development of extensive commercial and industrial facilities to maximise predominantly transport and logistical benefits to business, John Love identified an opportunity to capitalise on the increase in demand for the sale and management of commercial and industrial properties in the region.

Based upon this business opportunity, Love Commercial was established in 1997 and now offers a specialist service in Commercial and Industrial Real Estate from Footscray in Melbourne’s west, around the city’s northern fringe, to the Dandenong ranges in Melbourne’s east. A second office in Bayswater supports Love Commercial’s Headquarters in Reservoir. 

Love Commercial provides specialist services and professional advice regarding complex Commercial and Industrial Real Estate issues such as:


• The Goods and Services Tax (GST)
• Retail Tenancies Legislation
• Depreciation along with more complex building information and management systems
• Sales/Auctions/Leasing
• Property Management
• Certified Valuations etc

The team at Love Commercial prides itself on delivering specialist service and advice that is not only reliable, accurate and cost efficient, but most importantly, reflects an extensive knowledge of local market conditions.

We can help with any of these objectives.

Our confidential advice takes into account all of your property needs and personal concerns. It is important to thoroughly make sure that your property decisions are based on sound principals before you act.

We can assist and advise on investment properties, matrimonial disputes and partnership dissolutions, deceased estates and mortgagee's sales, commercial, industrial and business transactions.

Our service extends throughout the northern and eastern suburbs of Melbourne. With modern communications, mobile phones and the internet the 'local agent' syndrome went out years ago, so we are able to assist with your needs in any north-eastern, northern or eastern suburb. However, only qualified, experienced and competent estate agents can successfully achieve results consistently. We offer far more than just being a local agent.

Between 80-90% of our work is by way of either recommendation or referral. We always welcome new customers, so please give us a call if you are looking for a reliable service. Remember there is no substitute for quality service.

Independence

We are proudly an Australian owned independent office.

Most multi office groups rely on massive marketing (at your cost) and the 'glossy tag' of a network or franchise brand name. Therefore making their size a ‘perception’ only. Their 'one size fits all' formula is not suitable for many property owners.      

Smaller independent agencies can outperform most larger multi offices due to their more personal level of service, expertise and attention to detail.

COULTONS MELBOURNE is headed by Graham Coulton A.R.E.I  C.E.A. (R.E.I.V.) who supervises all the day to day activity of the business.

description:
If you’re buying, renting or selling a home, finding somebody to help do it right and do it your way – well, it’s a big deal. Quite literally one of the biggest deals you’ll make in your life.

?

To get the outcome you’re after, it takes knowhow, trust and heart. That’s why we position ourselves, with our hearts on our sleeve, as: friends; not agents, who sell homes; not houses. This shouldn’t come as a surprise, because we’ve always been this way, ever since our humble beginnings in 1924.We treat our clients as friends, and that’s why you can rely on us to be practical, honest, upfront and down-to-earth. There are no egos at Quixley – we are proud members of the community you live in.

?

But, don’t be fooled by our old-school values: our vision is to innovate, always. We consider our clients to be walking testimonials, and we are not satisfied unless we have exceeded their expectations. It’s about being passionate … but above all, consistent in our approach with everything property, particularly property in Melbourne.Whether you want to sell a family home in Alphington, buy a nineteenth-century-terrace in Fairfield, or lease out a renovated-warehouse in Richmond: the team here at Quixley are here to listen and help you buy, sell or rent your perfect Melbourne home.

?

So, if you’re looking for a real-estate agent that doesn’t really feel like a real-estate agent, try the one who has heart and more than 90 years’ experience.

Our team has vast experience and highly specialized training in the intricacies of sales and leasing for both residential and commercial properties, providing clients with a sense of ease during negotiations.

Our mission is to create value for our clients by combining extensive local knowledge and experience with established business relationships and marketing strategies.

Our team of professional agents are dynamic, experienced and dedicated to providing each client with the best solution for their real estate needs.

We approach all of our business opportunities with a team effort and believe in building long term relationships by employing high ethical standards and facilitating all transactions with a seamless service.
name: Naison Real Estate
Spencer Woods Real Estate

description:
At THE BISI AGENT we believe Real Estate could do with a shake up, so after nearly ten years working under a well-known franchise group, we knew it was time to separate ourselves from the pack and create a brand that was full of personality.

We’re not your typical run-of-the-mill agents - we offer a bespoke service unique to your needs and take the time to build a deep understanding and mutual respect with each one of our clients, whether you are a seller, landlord, buyer or tenant, we want you to feel THE BISI difference.

So, what makes us elite?

Our team is made of highly experienced, passionate and motivated mature professionals who know all facets of the industry intimately. Their biggest priority is to create an extraordinary experience which is uniquely tailored to your preferences, and we offer a full suite of services for you to pick from, too! 

We specialise in all aspects of Real Estate whether you are a vendor, landlord, buyer or tenant. No matter which service you’re looking for, our can do honest attitude and tailored service will never change - we want to work with you based on your preferences and make the experience an enjoyable one. We know it's important for you to know who you're trusting with the sale or management of your biggest investment , and we’ll make sure you get the best possible outcome. We’re best qualified to do it. In fact, our team was recognised as our previous franchise group’s leading office across sales and rentals for many years.

Imagine a personal assistant designed to anticipate your every need, guide you to the perfect home and ensure your complete satisfaction.

It’s not too far off. Our approach works. We have a brand new, striking and contemporary office run by Director John Bisignano, whose vision of innovation and forward thinking brings a breath of fresh air to your Real Estate experience. 

Come in and see what all the fuss is about today. We hope to meet you soon...
name: THE BISI AGENT

description:
Mayfair Property Management specialise in property management and commit ourselves to delivering an exceptional experience to our Investors (and their Tenants).

Our focus is on partnering with Investors to provide a productive, trouble free property investment experience that is built on extraordinary communication and personalised service.

We only accept top quality tenants who have been rigorously vetted. Getting a great tenant for your property and treating them with respect means that your property will be looked after, vacancies minimised and your return on investment will be above expectations.

We believe in creating and treasuring personal relationships. At Mayfair Property Management you will be dealing directly with the person who manages your property. You will know exactly who to call and who is in control of your valuable asset. Your personal property manager will be fully accountable.

Mayfair Property Management sets a new standard in the property management industry where excellent communication is the norm, fee structures are transparent, pro-active nurturing of your property and your tenants is expected and a stress free experience is delivered.
name: Mayfair Property Management

description:
Selecting Your Estate Agent

Selling a property can be a very emotional and stressful time. It is a huge decision for most of us whether it is our own personal home or an investment property.

Love Real Estate has been successfully selling and leasing property in your area since 1945. 

We understand the processes involved and the feelings that people have before, during and after the sale. 

We now sell to the children, grandchildren, nieces, nephews and friends of past clients.

This has been established over nearly six decades of tradition through our wholly owned independent localised seven-office network.  
 
 There’s every chance that your family has had a successful result with Love Real Estate as internal surveys show 62% of our clientele are repeat or referred customers. This is contributed to our ability to communicate at all levels and to cater for the linguistics of our community. Languages that are spoken at Love’s include Italian, Greek Yugoslav, Macedonian, Spanish, Arabic, Chinese, Vietnemese and English. 
 
At Love Real Estate we believe that to go into partnership with you, we as your agent have the following skills and knowledge to achieve the best possible result.

Loves provide professional expertise in;


Residential Sales

Property Management

Industrial and Commercial Sales, Leasing and Property

Management

Body Corporate Management

Valuations

Land Subdivision and Marketing

Special Projects
name: Love & Co Reservoir

description:
Since 1971 Nelson Alexander has stood for the highest possible levels of professional conduct as the only means to achieve consistently outstanding results.

We are not a franchise - we are one single team spread out over sixteen offices. Each of these are managed by senior partners and by working together to share ideas and knowledge we deliver the most comprehensive, dynamic and compelling real estate service in Melbourne's north.

We believe that our high-quality service is driven by a commitment to being trustworthy, transparent, and always having a serious and genuine regard for “doing the right thing”. Keeping our promises and acting with integrity are obligations we hold steadfast for our staff.

Our core values are based on unity and teamwork, and our unique structure allows us to work together to share ideas, knowledge and experience in order to deliver exceptional results.

Our connection with our local communities runs deep within our company’s culture, and we are proactive in delivering meaningful responses to the needs of worthwhile causes through the Nelson Alexander Charitable Foundation.

Nelson Alexander is truly the largest real estate agency in Melbourne’s northern suburbs. The sheer volume of transactions we conduct gives us vital insight and knowledge of what’s happening in the marketplace and therefore the ability to provide the most reliable and accurate advice for your next real estate transaction.

“Large Residential Agency of the Year 2020 (REIV)”
name: Nelson Alexander Reservoir

description:
Welcome to Ray Mascaro & Co. Pty Ltd Real Estate Service with Excellence Buying or Selling, Real Estate decisions are possibly the most important you will ever make.

Selecting the right agent to assist in this major transaction is therefore of vital importance. The office was established in 1968 by A. R. Butler since then the Company has continued to offer a Professional Real Estate Service. Our slogan now is "Real Estate Service With Excellence." This is our objective. Since 1971 under the Directorship of Mr. Ray Mascaro, the company has grown to be one of the industries leaders in the Northern Suburbs, specialising in all facets of residential and commercial real estate from sales and marketing to property management and investment. Why List With Us?

1. TOTAL COMMITMENT Because you put your confidence in us, we will provide you with the best professional assistance needed. We have proven commitment, honesty and dedication to our clients that will enable us to help make your real estate experience an enjoyable one.

2. KNOWLEDGE AND EXPERTISE All our staff are fully trained to the area, services and facilities. We have the expertise, education and training to professionally represent you in all your real estate needs.

3. PROFESSIONAL MARKETING PLAN AIn order to achieve the highest price, you need to market your home professionally. We can design an individual Marketing Plan to best suit your property. We offer all our advertising in "Full color print", including all our brochures in color. We will expose your property through 3 internet sites to better expose your property: realestate.com.au, realestateview.com.au and our own www.raymascaro.com.au

4. REGULAR FEEDBACK We will ensure that you are kept informed regularly on the progress and the interest created for your property.

5. SERVICE WITH EXCELLENCE The office was established in 1968 by A. R. Butler since then the Company has continued to offer a Professional Real Estate Service. Our slogan now is Real Estate Service With Excellence. This is our objectives.

6. SECURITY We will always inform you prior to any inspections carried out and any open for inspections that may be scheduled.

7. CONFIDENTIALITY When you engage us to act as your agent, we honor your privacy and keep all business dealings strictly confidential.

8. KNOW WHO YOU ARE DEALING WITH All negotiations will be handled through our office. You will be dealing with knowledgeable, responsible and experienced people who are authorized to act on your behalf.

description:
Love Commercial represents the natural expansion of the family run Love Real Estate residential network founded in 1945 by Mr E J Love.

The original office of Love Real Estate was established in the newly created Melbourne suburb of Reservoir, and with the rapid growth since then of Melbourne City to the North, Love Real Estate now has an additional 6 offices located in Thornbury, Preston, Thomastown, Mill Park and Epping.

With the further construction of Melbourne’s Western Ring Road and CityLink, and the resulting development of extensive commercial and industrial facilities to maximise predominantly transport and logistical benefits to business, John Love identified an opportunity to capitalise on the increase in demand for the sale and management of commercial and industrial properties in the region.

Based upon this business opportunity, Love Commercial was established in 1997 and now offers a specialist service in Commercial and Industrial Real Estate from Footscray in Melbourne’s west, around the city’s northern fringe, to the Dandenong ranges in Melbourne’s east. A second office in Bayswater supports Love Commercial’s Headquarters in Reservoir. 

Love Commercial provides specialist services and professional advice regarding complex Commercial and Industrial Real Estate issues such as:


• The Goods and Services Tax (GST)
• Retail Tenancies Legislation
• Depreciation along with more complex building information and management systems
• Sales/Auctions/Leasing
• Property Management
• Certified Valuations etc

The team at Love Commercial prides itself on delivering specialist service and advice that is not only reliable, accurate and cost efficient, but most importantly, reflects an extensive knowledge of local market conditions.
name: Love Commercial

Killen Thomas (Aust) Pty Ltd is an established Real Estate Practice whose history dates back to 1911 when it was established in New South Wales.

In 1992 a management buyout of Killen Thomas was effected by the current principals and directors to take the firm into todays highly competitive business environment thus creating a powerful and proactive real estate agency force.

With an enviable reputation as a full house agency, Killen Thomas have positioned themselves as an alternative to the larger and more inflexible agencies, and have achieved a pre-eminent and trustworthy respect within todays property and business community. 

At Killen Thomas, we aim to be different and establish policies which maintain the highest standards of real estate expertise and professionalism.

description:
Welcome to Harcourts, your northern suburbs property specialists, whose vast, multi-office network and strength as local market leaders have made them the company of choice in residential and commercial sales and leasing. Between their vast resources and those offered by the international Harcourts group, clients are given every available opportunity to make their property transactions a success. From powerful marketing with global reach, high-level training and professional development for all staff, cutting edge technology and advanced communications systems, this multi-lingual team is at the forefront of the industry while remaining sensitive to the specific needs of their community.

With approximately 70 staff spanning sales and auctioneering, property and asset management, marketing and administration, it’s a cohesive unit where complementary skills are pooled together to put clients’ interests first. Maintaining such high levels of professional excellence requires strong leadership from some of the most reputed names in the industry: Alex Doucas, Andrew DeSanto, Robert Ozzimo, Tony Lombardi, Daniel Taylor and John Georgiou.

Locals with massive combined experience and in-depth knowledge of the area, its people, the local property market and buyer demographics, the Harcourts team offer clients an unprecedented level of service, support, guidance and client care. This combines with an extremely successful sales history, expertise in negotiations and a mastery of the auction arena, resulting in record-breaking results and, of course the Number 3 spot Australia-wide from a pool of some 400 Australian offices. 

Despite having accumulated a large collection of prestigious industry awards in sales, auctioneering and property management, the team at Harcourts remain down-to-earth, warm and approachable. The original office of Love Real Estate was established in the newly created Melbourne suburb of Reservoir, and with the rapid growth since then of Melbourne City to the North, Love Real Estate now has an additional 6 offices located in Thornbury, Preston, Thomastown, Mill Park and Epping.

With the further construction of Melbourne’s Western Ring Road and CityLink, and the resulting development of extensive commercial and industrial facilities to maximise predominantly transport and logistical benefits to business, John Love identified an opportunity to capitalise on the increase in demand for the sale and management of commercial and industrial properties in the region.

Based upon this business opportunity, Love Commercial was established in 1997 and now offers a specialist service in Commercial and Industrial Real Estate from Footscray in Melbourne’s west, around the city’s northern fringe, to the Dandenong ranges in Melbourne’s east. A second office in Bayswater supports Love Commercial’s Headquarters in Reservoir. 

Love Commercial provides specialist services and professional advice regarding complex Commercial and Industrial Real Estate issues such as:


• The Goods and Services Tax (GST)
• Retail Tenancies Legislation
• Depreciation along with more complex building information and management systems
• Sales/Auctions/Leasing
• Property Management
• Certified Valuations etc

The team at Love Commercial prides itself on delivering specialist service and advice that is not only reliable, accurate and cost efficient, but most importantly, reflects an extensive knowledge of local market conditions.
name: Love Commercial

description:
Since 1971 Nelson Alexander has stood for the highest possible levels of professional conduct as the only means to achieve consistently outstanding results.

We are not a franchise - we are one single team spread out over sixteen offices. Each of these are managed by senior partners and by working together to share ideas and knowledge we deliver the most comprehensive, dynamic and compelling real estate service in Melbourne's north.

We believe that our high-quality service is driven by a commitment to being trustworthy, transparent, and always having a serious and genuine regard for “doing the right thing”. Keeping our promises and acting with integrity are obligations we hold steadfast for our staff.

Our core values are based on unity and teamwork, and our unique structure allows us to work together to share ideas, knowledge and experience in order to deliver exceptional results.

Our connection with our local communities runs deep within our company’s culture, and we are proactive in delivering meaningful responses to the needs of worthwhile causes through the Nelson Alexander Charitable Foundation.

Nelson Alexander is truly the largest real estate agency in Melbourne’s northern suburbs. The sheer volume of transactions we conduct gives us vital insight and knowledge of what’s happening in the marketplace and therefore the ability to provide the most reliable and accurate advice for your next real estate transaction.

“Large Residential Agency of the Year 2020 (REIV)”
name: Nelson Alexander Reservoir

description:
Choosing An Agency Is Tough... LetUs Convince You!

1. Save Up To 65% on Agent’s Fees

We believe the industry must accept a change in the way salespeople operate being an industry leader, Changing Places have introduced a “Fixed Fee” commission structure based on the general demographic of the buyer, and the level of effort and resources required to achieve the best possible outcome for our clients, not the dollar value of your property. Our unique business model allows us to reduce running costs without sacrificing our world-class service, therefore we choose to pass this saving onto our clients saving you up to 65% on typical agent’s fees.

2. Our Centralised Database

We are in constant communication with a vast number of qualified buyers each week. These buyers are entered into our centralized data management system can opt in to automatically advised of any new property listings that match their buying criteria. Unlike traditional agency networks, all of our Area Specialists have access to this national network of buyers, effectively allowing our salespeople to market your property on a national scale putting your property in front of more buyers each week.

More Buyers + Emotionally Connected + In Competition = Premium Price

3. Our National Network of Salespeople

We employ, train and support a National network of salespeople who are experts in their field and well networked within their territory. Our training is intense so we ensure each and every Area Specialist is fully equipped and capable to effectively manage the sale of your property.

4. Our Website

In today’s world over 85% of real estate business happens online. We provide a modern platform for buyers and sellers alike to obtain up-to-date information about the property market, industry trends and tips on buying and selling residential real estate. We are continually striving to push the limits of technology.

5. A Tailored Approach

We do not favour one sale method over another. The most effective method of sale can vary from suburb to suburb, state to state. It is our approach to act in the best interest of our clients and in too many cases a property is auctioned only to leave an owner ultimately disappointed. Our Experienced Area Specialists have an intimate knowledge of their marketplace and will submit their recommendations based on factual evidence and the individual needs of the property. Fact: Out of area and passive buyers are more likely to pay a premium price for a property!

6. Personal Service

In most real estate agencies, you start out with the Principal of the firm or a Senior Salesperson, however, you ultimately find the person who ends up handing your sale is far less experienced. With Changing Places, the Area Specialist is dedicated to your property from day one and stays with you right throughout the sale process.

7. Administration Support

By providing exceptional administration support to all of our Area Specialists we eliminate a large percentage of downtime allowing our salespeople to focus the majority of their energy on achieving the best result for our clients, spending more time working with potential buyers for your property.

8. Training & Development

We believe training is key to success – all our salespeople go through an initial induction program into our brand were we teach demonstrate how our unique philosophy and commission structure can help everyday sellers who are looking for a great real estate experience. In addition to this we provide access to ongoing training events and seminars to ensure our team are fully equipped with state-of-the-art tools, knowledge, and industry best practices ensuring the very best possible outcome can be achieved for our clients.

If you’re buying, renting or selling a home, finding somebody to help do it right and do it your way – well, it’s a big deal. Quite literally one of the biggest deals you’ll make in your life.

But, don’t be fooled by our old-school values: our vision is to innovate, always. It’s about being passionate … but above all, consistent in our approach with everything property, particularly property in Melbourne.Whether you want to sell a family home in Alphington, buy a nineteenth-century-terrace in Fairfield, or lease out a renovated-warehouse in Richmond: the team here at Quixley are here to listen and help you buy, sell or rent your perfect Melbourne home.

?

So, if you’re looking for a real-estate agent that doesn’t really feel like a real-estate agent, try the one who has heart and more than 90 years’ experience.

Mason White McDougall was established in 2001 and has been carefully nurtured into a successful ground roots family and community centred Real Estate Agency.  Mason White McDougall boasts a mature, experienced team, bringing a wealth of experience and local knowledge.  We are dedicated to excellence and good old fashioned service. We have lived and worked locally for many years and have an intimate knowledge of the area with a combined experience of over 200 years.  We are proud of our team's high personal standards of hard work, honesty and integrity.  We are committed to helping our clients achieve the best possible results and to achieve their Real Estate goals.  

Mason White McDougall has 4 offices strategically positioned in the Diamond Valley area including Diamond Creek, Hurstbridge, Kinglake and Whittlesea.
name: Mason White McDougall Hurstbridge

description: Boutique Agency operating across Melbourne.
name: Duncan McIntyre Real Estate

description:
Pitra Real Estate Group

Named as the emerging ‘new kids on the block’, Pitra Real Estate Group is making way in the Real Estate Industry.

Pitra Real Estate Group is a licensed agent. 100% Australian owned with high respect for their clientele needs and delivery of eminent customer service.

It is in their knowledge of experience and eagerness that thrives Pitra Real Estate Group to achieve top results for their clients.

Persistency and passion is the nature of Pitra Real Estate Group mesmerizing customers to keep them coming back. Fulfilling all their goals, requests & requirements from structure to $$$$$$ ensuring the best customer service!


Tom Pitra

Tom Pitra is the sole trader of Pitra Real Estate Group where the head office spands at the new stunning complex situated on the Ground Floor 215 Bell Street Preston.

Tom Pitra has been working in the industry since 2003 where he was involved selling properties all over Melbourne stretching from North, South, East and West suburbs ranging from residential-commercial-industrial and land for sub division. Tom plays a huge role in all facets of the business and he is highly respected within the industry.

Tom loves a challenge and is out there through sheer dedication providing his full attention with his outmost experience in this industry bringing people & property together.

Call Tom today  for your next Real Estate sale on 03 9422 5470 or 0421 972 028
name: Pitra Real Estate Group

description: Client service is an integral part of real estate in today's competitive environment. The Reservoir office of the Barry Plant Group has been servicing the local community for over 43 years and has developed a strong team of real estate professionals. Whether you are intending to buy, sell or lease a property, seek the advice of the areas most innovative real estate network, the Barry Plant Group. Inspect all of our properties for sale or rent from this Internet site and phone or e-mail should you require any additional information or advice.  Our 75 strong office network is here to help you.  Call us today and allow us to show you the Red Carpet Experience.
name: Barry Plant Reservoir

description:
Millership & Co opened in 2000 and through its commitment to high standards and quality customer service has become the area's most successful independant agency.

We offer a full range of real estate services including Sales, free market appraisals and property management.

Call or email us for the very best advice regarding your property needs.
name: Millership & Co

description:
Ray White South Morang is a thriving business in Melbourne’s northern growth corridor.

Specialising in Residential and Commercial Sales, Residential and Commercial Leasing and Financial Services, Ray White South Morang is an impressive team of professionals who remain at the forefront of technology, marketing and training which translates to exceptional results for our clients. Dedicated to excellence the team is respected for their honesty and ethical approach, as well as their professionalism and superior customer service.

Situated in the City Of Whittlesea, the area offers a mix of country town, rural farm, and suburban housing all of which our experienced sales team excel.

Ray White South Morang is part of Australasia’s largest Real Estate Group, enhancing our marketing knowledge with a worldwide database network, and together with our local knowledge, we achieve premium results for our clients.

To enquire on how we can help you achieve you real estate goals, contact our office on 03 9404 1222.
name: Ray White South Morang

description: Appleby Real Estate have been at the forefront of the property industry in Melbourne’s east since 1963. Today, this second-generation business continues to grow and expand their services, to ensure client's maximise their return and fulfil their property ambitions. Managing Director Nick Draffin is dedicated and passionate about the company, the brand and the level of service Appleby deliver, offering an unsurpassed standard of sales and property management services. With unmatched local knowledge, formidable negotiation skills and an expansive network of industry contacts acquired over 59 years, the Appleby team is well equipped to out-perform any competition.
name: Appleby Real Estate

Servicing the Knox Community & Surrounds Since 1963


Appleby Real Estate has been at the forefront of the property industry in Melbourne's east since 1963.

Today, our second generation business continues to grow and expand our services, to ensure our clients maximise their return and fulfil their property ambitions.

Managing Director Nick Draffin is dedicated and passionate about the company, the brand and the level of service Appleby deliver, offering an unsurpassed standard of sales and asset management services.

With unmatched local knowledge, formidable negotiation skills and an expansive network of industry contacts acquired over almost 60 years, the Appleby team is well equipped to out-perform any competition.

 

We are all about people......It's not a job, it's our passion.
name: R.E. Appleby Pty Ltd

description:
Specialising in Residential Sales, Residential Leasing and Financial Services, Ray White Bayswater is an impressive young team of professionals who remain at the forefront of technology, marketing and training which translates to exceptional results for our clients. Dedicated to excellence the team is respected for their honesty and ethical approach, as well as their professionalism and superior customer service.

 

Situated on the fringe of the City Of Knox & City of Maroondah, these areas offer a great mix of suburban housing all of which our experienced sales & rental teams excel.

 

Ray White Bayswater is part of Australasia’s largest Real Estate Group, enhancing our marketing knowledge with a worldwide database network, and together with our local knowledge, we achieve premium results for our clients.

To enquire on how we can help you achieve you real estate goals, contact our office on 03 8727 6200.
name: Ray White Bayswater

description:
Boronia is one of the many suburbs to be found in the 'the most liveable City' – Knox. A vibrant and modern area nestled against the picturesque backdrop of the Dandenong Ranges. The Boronia area continues to build on its strengths of community, business and commitment to the environment.

Boronia boasts an array of lifestyle opportunities for you and your families, including a choice of excellent private and government schools, a tertiary college, reliable public transport and the second largest shopping centre in Australia, Knox City.

With over 350 specialty stores, Knox City together with Knox Ozone provides a unique shopping, entertainment, leisure and dining experience.

Mark Schroeder and the team at Barry Plant Boronia provide a marketing edge to vendors by placing their properties before more buyers everyday. They do this by tapping into the Melbourne wide Barry Plant network which includes working closely with the neighbouring offices of Rowville and Wantirna.

At Barry Plant Boronia, we feel that being entrusted to help sell or purchase your greatest financial asset is a huge privilege and responsibility. Therefore, our ultimate aim is to make the whole experience of buying or selling real estate as enjoyable and stress free as possible every time. Occasionally someone experiences a stress free home sale by accident. We’re here to make it happen on purpose.

Boronia's dynamic teamwork, negotiation skills and their high standards of personal client attention make them the strongest force in the Knox area.

"What lies before us and what lies beyond us is tiny compared to what lies within us – It's not just another property.....It's your home and we'll treat it that way"
name: Barry Plant Boronia

description: In an increasingly fast-paced world, we know that while people want the most professional efficient service, they still prize the fundamentals of honesty and integrity from real estate consultants committed to achieving their clients’ goals. That’s why at Harcourts Boronia we combine world-renowned technology, training and systems with a focus on establishing trust and respect with our clients who always remain at the centre of the process. Whether you’re buying or selling established residential property or land, or you are an investor requiring professional property management services, at Harcourts Boronia we’re proud to say we put the focus on Global. National. Local. and most importantly, You.
name: Harcourts Boronia

description: Max Brown Croydon is an integral office forming part of the highly successful Max Brown Real Estate Group. Since 1958, the Max Brown brand continues to lead the market by providing personal service, dedication, skill, experience and a team approach. Our team has every sector of the real estate market covered. From our sales team, project development team and property management team, our results speak for themselves. For all your real estate needs, please contact us for sound, reliable advice
name: Max Brown Real Estate Group

description:
WHO ARE WE?

We are just like you. We're people who live locally, raise families, interact with the local community, serve on school committees and play local sport. We are also agents and we are all about making real estate real again.

No pretensions or game playing. We bring a wealth of experience and marketing expertise sourced from some of the best in the world. We have travelled far and wide to find what works and what doesn’t in real estate sales and we have learned from some of the best practitioners on the planet. We want you to benefit from that experience.

Our core belief is that you, our client, deserve only the best. The best agents, the best support staff, the best technology and the best information to make your sale the most rewarding it can be.

We also believe in fun mixed in with our hard work. We don’t take ourselves too seriously and we want you to feel comfortable in your dealings with us every step of the way. Our office layout has been carefully designed to ensure that anyone who walks through our doors will find a comfortable and non-threatening atmosphere in which to do business. 
We’ll provide the coffee and all you need to bring is an open mind and a willingness to be bold and exciting. We are Market Share Property and we’re here to show you how to Buy. Sell. Better.
name: Market Share Property

description:
Out performing, Over achieving...

Ray White Manningham is a Real Estate agency with a reputation for excellence, housing some of Victorias finest Agents. We pride ourselves on our professionalism and exceptional customer service. Whether its assistance with Residential Sales and Rentals, Commercial Sales, Leasing, Property Management or even Home Loans, our extensive experience will ensure our clients make the right choice. Our Award Winning, highly trained and motivated Sales Team provide a service that keeps our clients informed and supported. With a unique understanding and knowledge of the local market we are renowned for achieving great results.
name: Ray White Manningham

description:
FOR ALL YOUR REAL ESTATE NEEDS WITH A PERSONAL TOUCH 
 
A boutique business since 2001 and conducted with total dedication to first class quality service, all properties listed for sale and rental are given total attention. Specializing in Residential Sales, Rentals and Buyer's Advocate. We offer free property appraisals.

We are pleased to be of assistance to you and extend our co-operation, advice and service. We are keen to discuss the finer points in the marketing of your property, such as:

  • A relevant marketing method you may choose...
  • An advertising campaign that will benefit your needs...
  • A total awareness during the marketing of your property...
  • An experience that you will tell others about...
  • A Buyer Advocacy approach for Expat or Overseas buyer needs ...

Whenever you are ready to sell or rent out your property, I will be very pleased to hear from you and help you make the necessary arrangements.
 
We thank you in advance for allowing our company to inspect your property with a view to giving an assessment of its current market value. We are pleased to be of assistance to you and extend our co-operation, advice and service.

For more details please phone Andre Chin on 9842 8708 OR 0421087961 ALL HOURS
name: Acres & Sons Pty Ltd

address2: Cnr Burwood Hwy & Ferntree Gully Rd
description:
Our office was established in Ferntree Gully in mid 1970’s when the local area was expanding in leaps and bounds. The farmland was being developed into housing estates with allotments ranging from 750sqm to 1000sqm. As the population grew, businesses grew to meet the population’s demands. 1980 – 1990 was the growth decade in both residential, commercial and industrial when Ferntree Gully and the Knox area as a whole was transformed into a more modern and vibrant area.

 

Abley Real Estate joined the Professionals Real Estate Group as one of their first members’s well over 30 years ago as it was 100% Australian owned and operated. Today the group has well over 300 offices and has expanded to New Zealand, throughout South East Asia area and now looking to the United State of America. The group prides itself on its social responsibility through office contribution at local and national levels, as a key supporter to the National Breast Cancer Foundation and the Child Cancer Foundation.

 

Ray Abley is also renowned for his generosity to local sporting and community groups for junior sports for nearly 30 years.

 

Abley Real Estate Pty Ltd is known for the stability of their staff when most senior staff has been established for 15 – 20 years.

 

The office have specialised staff in the following categories.

a)            Residential Sales

b)            Residential Property Management

c)            Commercial Industrial Leasing & Sales

d)            Project Management in developments and constructions

e)            Buyers advocate service

 

You can feel confident when you appoint Abley Real Estate Pty Ltd to handle all your property needs because we have the necessary experienced staff with a minimum of 15 years experience. Our office has been voted Number One Real Estate Agency of the year in Knox on a number of occasions.
name: Abley Real Estate Pty Ltd

description:
Ray White Real Estate Ferntree Gully

Ray White Ferntree Gully enjoys a high community profile with an excellent position on Ferntree Gully Road next door to Fernwood Gym.
At Ray White Ferntree Gully we work as a team to offer maximum coverage to our clients in the sale & management of their property, enabling us to achieve excellent results for our landlords and top prices for our vendors. 
We believe that solid and ethical work practices based on continual communication with our clients is the only way to work. Much of our business comes from referrals as we aim to build our business and provide a complete Real Estate Service with honesty and integrity at its foundation.
name: Ray White Ferntree Gully

description:
Stockdale & Leggo Ferntree Gully is a leading member of the Stockdale & Leggo franchise group, Victoria’s largest, consisting of approximately 80 offices state-wide.  The Stockdale & Leggo group has been delivering real estate services to the people of Victoria for over 75 years, beginning from a single office in Glenhuntly around 1934.

The Ferntree Gully office,  as you now see it, began in 1996.  Under the careful eye of Paul Stone, Director and Tom Tsiagalos, Sales Manager, the office has grown into the market leader it is today.  The business offers “everything real estate” from Sales and Auctions to Property Management for both Residential and Commercial properties. 

Currently employing dedicated staff, the Ferntree Gully office includes a Sales Team actively listing and selling property, Residential Property Managers and a very professional team of Administration staff providing behind-the-scenes support.

Under the management of Tom Tsiagalos, his team is making its mark within this high traffic location.  With thousands of people per week visiting the Mountain Gate Shopping Centre and frontage to Burwood Highway, the exposure has provided an even greater profile for the business and more importantly our vendors.The success story of the Ferntree Gully office has been quite phenomenal. 

Not only has the office enjoyed a tremendous record over a long period, but many of our Sales and Rental staff have achieved outstanding results over the same time.  Paul Stone and Tom Tsiagalos have both established themselves within this “service hungry” industry with outstanding results over an extended period.

per
name: Stockdale & Leggo Ferntree Gully

description:
The team at Schroeder & Wallis are real estate experts within the City of Knox. We offer an unmatched level of service to all our clients no matter what your property requirements are.

 

What makes us unique is the proactive nature of our entire approach to servicing your property needs. We wear our passion for real estate on our sleeve and constantly assess and reassess the effectiveness of our campaigns with a view to improving and embracing innovation and creative thinking to guarantee outstanding results. We are highly analytical, anticipating individual needs and applying our market insights to deliver the best result for people buying, selling or leasing property.

 

The service we provide at Schroeder & Wallis is defined by passion and integrity. Combining award-winning, large-scale thinking with a commitment to tailored client care we strive to exceed expectations at all times. Above all else, our service is effective. Our specialist expertise, market knowledge and impeccable attention to detail achieve strong returns for our steady client base.
name: Schroeder & Wallis

description:
Ray White Lilydale
 
Ray White Lilydale isn't just another real estate office. Sure, it has the premium location right in the heart of Main Street with plenty of parking right out the front. And yes, the office is beautifully presented and has the latest electronic window displays that run 24/7.
 
But where the difference comes in is with commitment and experience. As a part of the international Ray White group of more than 700 offices, Ray White Lilydale has vast array of resources available.
 
There's also the network of surrounding offices and the sort of knowledge that comes from an organisation that was founded more than 100 years ago in 1902, and prides itself on leading the way with technology and always moving with the times.
 
And then there are the people, headed up by Graham Reynolds, and Sales Manager Bruno Cascianelli. Both of them are well known identities in the area; Ray White Lilydale has a reputation for its people.
 
Highly trained and very experienced, they don't just talk real estate, they know it first hand, with all the local events, places and everything else that makes Lilydale and the Yarra Valley such a great place to live and work.
 
Call in today and meet the team from Ray White Lilydale. You'll find our high profile office at 164 Main Street Lilydale, just near the corner of Hutchinson Street and opposite the Olinda Creek Hotel.
 
Or, you may wish to phone us on 9735 5050
name: Ray White Lilydale

description:
Fusion Property Investment Corporation is one of the leading service providers for property investment in Melbourne. Through our philosophy, “Better Investment, Better Life”, coupled with our platform of resources, local real estate experience and expertise, we guide our clients to maximize their investment return and growth. Fusion Property, operating under the management of Fusion Realty Development Group, works closely with over twenty Australian real estate developers and project marketers, we have planned and managed successful marketing campaigns in Asia for many renowned Australian developers.

Specializing in real estate investment, our services cover all aspects of the property industry, we offer “tailored strategic investing advice” to our valued customers, always placing safety and security of their investment as our first and foremost objective.

Fusion Property understands the market cycle and trends in the Australian property market like no other realty group. Our expertise, coupled with an in depth appreciation of our clients’ personal needs, affordability, financial status and goals, enables us to offer the optimal property advice to our valued clients. Fusion property is committed to using our local knowledge to provide the optimal project to each and every one of our customers, to ensure your return in partnership with our professional services.
name: Fusion Property Investment Corporation

description: Responding to the needs of an ever increasing clientele in the Maroondah area and across into Knox, Bell Real Estate are back in Montrose, covering the outer eastern suburbs of Montrose, Mt Evelyn, Lilydale, Mooroolbark and reaching back into Kilsyth, Kilsyth South, The Basin, Bayswater, Bayswater North, Croydon and even Ringwood. Displaying a commitment to Customer Service never before seen in this area, the highly trained staff working out of the Montrose office welcome the opportunity to meet and exceed your expectations in all facets of real estate. With Registered Builders, Licensed Real Estate Agents, and Property Management expertise spanning more than 40 years, with one call you’re able to access friendly valuable advice to assist you in making informed decisions regarding the improvement, selling or management of your most valuable asset. Commencing operations in the Eastern suburbs in the early 70’s Sydney Bell followed by his sons Chris and Trevor Bell and daughter Rosalie have continued a tradition of personalized service which is a hallmark of the Bell brand. Third generation agent and Sales Manager of the Montrose office Ryan Bell is a Registered Builder and renovator. Ryan has all the qualities of an exceptional team member who will achieve outstanding results for all of his clients. Your choice of agent is an important one. At Bell Real Estate guarantee of service and ethical standards are of the highest calibre. We look forward to assisting you with all of your real estate needs.
name: Bell Real Estate Montrose

description: Sue Jackson and her team take pride in offering our local area the ultimate service in real estate. Having lived in the Montrose area for some time, Sue & her team are truly passionate about Montrose & the surrounding areas. The Max Brown office in Montrose offers friendly, professional service. There is no task too big or too small for this team. Sue & her team over many, many years, have consistently achieved premium results for their clients. They are the number one agency in the local area! True success in real estate doesn't just come from selling properties it comes from being honest, understanding and loyal.
name: Max Brown - Montrose

description:
The Methven organisation has been established in the area for over 40 years and enjoys a reputation of honesty, integrity and market leadership, derived from achieving outstanding results for our clients. 

The Directors are Shane Lowe, Geoff Earney, Greg Earney and John Manning, each with many years experience and a background of Community and Real Estate Institute involvement. They head a team of 25 trained Sales Consultants operating out of 4 prominent offices and are backed by the Australian and New Zealand wide Real Estate Professionals Group of over 450 branches a constant source of referrals working to introduce more buyers to your property. 

Details of every property listed are provided to our 4 offices and buyers may be introduced by all members of our Sales Team of 25 representatives.

description:
Grandstand Real Estate has been established since 2015. As an independent real estate agency, Grandstand has been servicing all areas of Melbourne. Since its establishment, Grandstand has successfully leased and/or sold properties in Melbourne sought after locations including Burwood, Camberwell, Doncaster, Ferntree Gully, Glen Waverley, Kew, Knoxfield, Malvern, Melbourne CBD, Mitcham, Mount Waverley, Ringwood, Rowville, Scoresby, South Yarra, Wantirna, Wantirna South, Wheelers Hill and so on.

We are a dynamic and multi-cultural team that strives to achieve grand outcomes for our clients with dedication and integrity. With a CLIENT-CENTRIC approach in everything we do, we actively listen to our clients’ needs, carefully plan and organize our tasks, and effectively carry out actions to deliver the best outcomes for our clients.

Conan Ong, the director of Grandstand, has more than 25 years of real estate experience. As director, Conan believes in leading by example. His career history can be measured by literally hundreds of property transactions, many of which have delivered outcomes to his clients far above their expectations. We STAND with our clients for GRAND outcomes. Together we GRAND, together we STAND.
name: Grandstand Real Estate

description:
Lawson Real Estate was established in 1990 by Steven Lawson as a specialist Industrial Commercial Retail agency with emphasis on serving the Eastern and South Eastern market.

Conveniently located in Mount Waverley, our office is within minutes to most industrial areas having immediate access to the South Eastern Freeway and major North South arterial roads.

Lawson Real Estate Pty Ltd has grown to be a recognised force in this specialised market providing Sales, Leasing, Property Management and Consulting services.

Our extensive computerised systems, include both property management and our unique Listings/Sales database with in excess of 5,500 individual property details, this enables our office to undertake extensive direct marketing and have access to detailed property information unavailable to others.

A major difference and advantage that our office has over many agencies is that we place great importance on teamwork within the office, ensuring that all information and potential opportunities are maximised
name: Lawson Real Estate

description:
With numerous local area experts and a long list of recent sales in the area, it was a natural progression for Fletchers to open an office right in the heart of thriving Ringwood.

The vibrant team are lead by Director Reilly Waterfield who has an enthusiastic and ambitious approach to real estate and extensive knowledge about Maroondah.

The City of Maroondah is located 23 kilometres from the CBD and is well-known for its picturesque tree-lined streets and abundance of parks and reserves. Recently, the City of Maroondah has attracted many investors with numerous large-scale commercial developments underway, making it a booming suburban metropolis.

Our new office is centrally located so please drop in and introduce yourself to our friendly team- the door is always open!
name: Fletchers Maroondah

description:
Corporate Profile

When you list your home with Century 21 Unlimited in Ringwood East, you will be supported by a team of highly trained professionals, who are all dedicated to achieving the successful sale of your property. We recognise that your decision to sell is one of the biggest decisions in your life, so it's important to us that you receive the best customer service.

We fulfil this promise by keeping you informed. No matter which service we're providing, we will keep you up-to-date with constant communication and open dialogue. You can rely on our team, because we have all been trained - and continue to be trained - with the best industry systems on offer.

A good team is a competitive team and we at Century 21 Unlimited Ringwood East are a great team. We're always looking for ways to surpass the industry standard and consistently embrace new ideas and technology in order to serve you better.

In addition to this, you may already have the peace of mind of knowing some of our esteemed team members. This is because many of them have lived in the local area for years and knows from firsthand experience what it's like to buy and sell in the Eastern and Outer Eastern area.
name: Century 21 Unlimited

description:
At Ray White Rowville we work harder for our customers.

Backed with over 116 years of experience from Australasia’s largest real estate group, Ray White Rowville clients can rest assured that they have selected the right team.

Having established themselves as market leaders in the Knox area, we know firsthand what makes the area and the lifestyle attractive. What’s more, we know what motivates buyers in the local market.

Our comprehensive past client and buyer database ensures that your property is presented to more genuine buyers, to maximise the competition to buy your property. During the campaign, we use a refined set of processes that have been specifically designed to get you the best possible price for your property.

When you choose an agent at Ray White Rowville, you get the support of our full team. Our unique structure encourages all agents to work together to achieve the best price for your property. With over 1,000 offices across 11 countries, we can also connect you to buyers from all over the world. This international exposure is an added dimension no other agency can rival.

We pride ourselves on providing an exceptional level of personal and professional service to make the selling process easy and rewarding for all our clients.
name: Ray White Rowville

description:
When it comes to selling or leasing commercial property it is best to entrust it to hockingstuart Commercial – the people who have the necessary know-how and experience to expertly handle these highly specialised transactions for you.

 hockingstuart’s Commercial division deals in commercial properties in all suburbs and constantly monitors sales results and rental levels across the board so their clients can have ready access to the most up-to-the-minute information at all times.

 Our team is thoroughly conversant with the complexities of leases, the implications of the GST and the associated legal requirements associated with commercial real estate.
name: Belle Property Commercial South Melbourne

description:
Wantirna is one of the many suburbs to be found in the 'the most liveable City' – Knox. A vibrant and modern area nestled against the picturesque backdrop of the Dandenong Ranges. The Wantirna area continues to build on its strengths of community, business and commitment to the environment. Wantirna boasts an array of lifestyle opportunities for you and your families, including a choice of excellent private and government schools, a tertiary college, reliable public transport and the second largest shopping centre in Australia, Knox City. With over 350 specialty stores, Knox City together with Knox Ozone provides a unique shopping, entertainment, leisure and dining experience.

Brendan Murphy, Adam Sorrell and the team at Barry Plant Wantirna provide a marketing edge to vendors by placing their properties before more buyers everyday. They do this by tapping into the Melbourne wide Barry Plant network which includes working closely with the neighbouring offices of Rowville and Boronia. At Barry Plant Wantirna, we feel that being entrusted to help sell or purchase your greatest financial asset is a huge privilege and responsibility. Therefore, our ultimate aim is to make the whole experience of buying or selling real estate as enjoyable and stress free as possible every time. Occasionally someone experiences a stress free home sale by accident. We’re here to make it happen on purpose. Wantirna's dynamic teamwork, negotiation skills and their high standards of personal client attention make them the strongest force in the Knox area. "What lies before us and what lies beyond us is tiny compared to what lies within us – It's not just another property....It's your home and we’ll treat it that way"
name: Barry Plant Wantirna

description:
Cameron. is a successful and dominant company with a fine reputation and a strong team of sales, leasing and administration staff dedicated to producing outstanding results.

The cornerstone of our success has been our comprehensive knowledge and commitment to the South East Industrial/Commercial market. This knowledge developed over 40 years of hands on, on the ground dedication to a specific market place has given us the edge over national and local based competition.

Cameron. services our large base of clients from two offices based in Dandenong South and Wantirna.
name: Cameron - Eastern Office

description:
First National Real Estate Wantirna is the real estate specialist for Wantirna, Knoxfield, Wantirna South, Bayswater and surrounds. Providing real estate services ranging from residential sales, property management to commercial real estate sales and lease, First National Real Estate Wantirna can help you with all your real estate needs.

At First National Real Estate Wantirna, you will always be treated as our top priority. At First National Real Estate Wantirna – we put you first.
name: First National Real Estate Wantirna

description:
We are a progressive family owned real estate agency offering a genuinely personal level of service, while at the same time delivering the highest standard of professional real estate service and expertise.  Our company focus is on residential property management services and real estate sales within the City of Knox and surrounding Melbourne suburbs.  Our success as an ‘independent’ real estate agency has been built on the personal referral of business from past satisfied clients, tenants and landlords together with our outstanding reputation and local knowledge.

Hill Real Estate and all Hill Real Estate staff are members of the Real Estate Institute of Victoria and has suitably qualified and professionally motivated employees to enable us to guarantee a constantly high standard of personal real estate service. Our office is conveniently located on Burwood Highway, in the white terraces opposite Knox City Shopping Centre.
name: Hill Real Estate

description:
Experienced and strong performing in any market, Professionals Wantirna are highly regarded for their tenacity in achieving premium results and conscientious regard for their clients.

Established in 2001 with a commitment to excellence, Professionals Wantirna have a reputation as top performers in sales, projects, auctions, property leasing and management. We love what we do and we do it with passion, drive, excellence and enthusiasm. Referrals and repeat business from happy clients are keys to our success.

Working together as part of a 300 office network with a multi-lingual team, we employ marketing strategies that connect with people locally and internationally. We are invested in building authentic relationships with clients at every price point.

We know Knox. Our families grew up here and we view the eastern suburbs as the most liveable and desirable. We are proud to support the local community by assisting with school functions, sporting events, fetes, fundraisers and donating to the National Breast Cancer Foundation from every sale. As NBCF’s Diamond Partner, Professionals have raised over $3,000,000 and counting.

Our determination to remain customer focused is supported by our attention to detail, unrivalled knowledge, proven marketing strategies, advanced technologies, professionalism and refined negotiating skills to outpace the competition.

Our goal is to create customer happiness and help you achieve your real estate dream.
name: Professionals Wantirna

description:
Ray White Wantirna has established itself as Wantirna’s market leader in quality Real Estate services. Director Zac Clancey and the team of uncompromising Real Estate professionals ensure first class service to all Ray White Wantirna clients.

Ray White Wantirna is strategically located at the Studfield Shopping Centre where several thousand shoppers pass by the window weekly and is consistently a top ten office in the network of over 100 Ray White offices. For obligation free advice whether you are buying, selling, renting or looking to have your investment property professionally managed, call us today.

Our focus is entirely on our clients. We believe that success is built on the strength of the relationships we forge and all of our dedicated agents share our same vision and quest for excellence.

Our services include:

  • Residential sales
  • Residential land sales
  • Residential Rentals

    •
name: Ray White Wantirna

description: If you're looking to put your home on the market for any reason, come to the professionals who will provide you with the highest level of client service - something you should not hope for, but expect when making such a decision. Our team here at OBrien Real Estate Wantirna will deliver top-tier professional property solutions right across the board, whether you're buying, selling, renting or leasing.
name: OBrien Real Estate Wantirna

description:
Boronia is one of the many suburbs to be found in the 'the most liveable City' – Knox. A vibrant and modern area nestled against the picturesque backdrop of the Dandenong Ranges. The Boronia area continues to build on its strengths of community, business and commitment to the environment.

Boronia boasts an array of lifestyle opportunities for you and your families, including a choice of excellent private and government schools, a tertiary college, reliable public transport and the second largest shopping centre in Australia, Knox City.

With over 350 specialty stores, Knox City together with Knox Ozone provides a unique shopping, entertainment, leisure and dining experience.

Mark Schroeder and the team at Barry Plant Boronia provide a marketing edge to vendors by placing their properties before more buyers everyday. They do this by tapping into the Melbourne wide Barry Plant network which includes working closely with the neighbouring offices of Rowville and Wantirna.

At Barry Plant Boronia, we feel that being entrusted to help sell or purchase your greatest financial asset is a huge privilege and responsibility. Therefore, our ultimate aim is to make the whole experience of buying or selling real estate as enjoyable and stress free as possible every time. Occasionally someone experiences a stress free home sale by accident. We’re here to make it happen on purpose.

Boronia's dynamic teamwork, negotiation skills and their high standards of personal client attention make them the strongest force in the Knox area.

"What lies before us and what lies beyond us is tiny compared to what lies within us – It's not just another property.....It's your home and we'll treat it that way"
name: Barry Plant Boronia

description:
iTRAK is moving you with the times......

iTRAK Real Estate was born from a need to offer Home Sellers a far more relevant service, one that is in line with modern technology. We provide the most efficient way to sell your home.

Our efficiency stems from an understanding of modern buyer research behavior which translates into a business model that keeps overheads and costs low

The internet has been the most powerful change to the real estate industry ever. It's changed the way buyers search for properties. It also has resulted in a massive change to just how much competition Home Sellers can attract on their home. Using a smart and professional sales strategy a well presented home can generate upwards of 100 buyer inspections in the first two weeks.

Founding Director David Stewart has established a team of like minded and experienced Agents;who can offer Home Sellers professional guidance and strategies to generate a Premium Price with the benefit of saving money. iTRAK is proud of the difference we are already making for so many Home Sellers; having already sold homes in over 50 Melbourne suburbs. We look forward to speaking to you any time; whether selling your home or taking care of your investment property.
name: Biggin & Scott Boronia

National. Local. and most importantly, You.
