description: In an increasingly fast-paced world, we know that while people want the most professional efficient service, they still prize the fundamentals of honesty and integrity from real estate consultants committed to achieving their clients’ goals. That’s why at Harcourts Boronia we combine world-renowned technology, training and systems with a focus on establishing trust and respect with our clients who always remain at the centre of the process. Whether you’re buying or selling established residential property or land, or you are an investor requiring professional property management services, at Harcourts Boronia we’re proud to say we put the focus on Global. National. Local. and most importantly, You.
name: Harcourts Boronia

description:
We are a boutique real estate agency who focus on investment properties. Our extensive network of professionals are able to help you find the right property for your investment requirements. We also work with a wide range of professionals ie. mortgage broker and financial planner to properly structure the investment framework that will lay a foundation for you for compounding growth of properties. We work with accountant to work out your finances with you and the best way to minimise tax on your investment property whether it is positively gear or negatively gear strategy that you had chosen.

You will find that at Cuspac Property Group we are not a typical real estate agent. We are about building relationship, whether you have a need in term of finance, in term of legal questions or construction matter, we will be there with you to find the suitable professional to come out a solution for you in your investment journey.

To many people buying or selling a property is a BIG thing, and we take this seriously. It is not just about a transaction, we care about you and want to be a partner with you in your investment journey. For us it is about making friendship. My sincere hope is that everyone that come into and have associated with us before is enriched through our meeting. 

Once you had purchased a property from us we will also help you manage it and thus give you more time to focus on the investment side of things on your next property venture.

We also speak a variety of languages from English, Mandarin, Cantonese, Malay and Indonesian.

If you feel anything that you want to chat about in term of property, please do feel free to give me a call at (03) 8678 1808, so that we can schedule a time for a tea or coffee.

 I wish you all the best in this year in your investment journey.

Sincerely,

Joshua Chong

Officer in Effective Control 

CEO
name: Cuspac Property Group

description:
Melbourne 1 Real Estate is an independent, family owned real estate firm offering a personalized and professional real estate with full range of services to local and foreign investors, buyers. We always take pride in our business and always strive to provide both professional services and up to date knowledge to achieve the best possible results for all our clients. Honesty and respect are two qualities which we will always continue to uphold and encourage within our team environment.
Whether you’re a client or a team member, we will never let you down. Our well-informed, hard working and energetic team covers general residential real estate sales and property management, rural and special rural property sales, commercial and industrial sales, leasing and business sales.
We have many serious buyers from the overseas market.
name: Melbourne 1 Real Estate

description:
FOR ALL YOUR REAL ESTATE NEEDS WITH A PERSONAL TOUCH 
 
A boutique business since 2001 and conducted with total dedication to first class quality service, all properties listed for sale and rental are given total attention. Specializing in Residential Sales, Rentals and Buyer's Advocate. We offer free property appraisals.

We are pleased to be of assistance to you and extend our co-operation, advice and service. We are keen to discuss the finer points in the marketing of your property, such as:

  • A relevant marketing method you may choose...
  • An advertising campaign that will benefit your needs...
  • A total awareness during the marketing of your property...
  • An experience that you will tell others about...
  • A Buyer Advocacy approach for Expat or Overseas buyer needs ...

Whenever you are ready to sell or rent out your property, I will be very pleased to hear from you and help you make the necessary arrangements.
 
We thank you in advance for allowing our company to inspect your property with a view to giving an assessment of its current market value. We are pleased to be of assistance to you and extend our co-operation, advice and service.

For more details please phone Andre Chin on 9842 8708 OR 0421087961 ALL HOURS
name: Acres & Sons Pty Ltd

description:
Ray White Real Estate Ferntree Gully

Ray White Ferntree Gully enjoys a high community profile with an excellent position on Ferntree Gully Road next door to Fernwood Gym.
At Ray White Ferntree Gully we work as a team to offer maximum coverage to our clients in the sale & management of their property, enabling us to achieve excellent results for our landlords and top prices for our vendors. 
We believe that solid and ethical work practices based on continual communication with our clients is the only way to work. Much of our business comes from referrals as we aim to build our business and provide a complete Real Estate Service with honesty and integrity at its foundation.
name: Ray White Ferntree Gully

description:
Stockdale & Leggo Ferntree Gully is a leading member of the Stockdale & Leggo franchise group, Victoria’s largest, consisting of approximately 80 offices state-wide.  The Stockdale & Leggo group has been delivering real estate services to the people of Victoria for over 75 years, beginning from a single office in Glenhuntly around 1934.

The Ferntree Gully office,  as you now see it, began in 1996.  Under the careful eye of Paul Stone, Director and Tom Tsiagalos, Sales Manager, the office has grown into the market leader it is today.  The business offers “everything real estate” from Sales and Auctions to Property Management for both Residential and Commercial properties. 

Currently employing dedicated staff, the Ferntree Gully office includes a Sales Team actively listing and selling property, Residential Property Managers and a very professional team of Administration staff providing behind-the-scenes support.

Under the management of Tom Tsiagalos, his team is making its mark within this high traffic location.  With thousands of people per week visiting the Mountain Gate Shopping Centre and frontage to Burwood Highway, the exposure has provided an even greater profile for the business and more importantly our vendors.The success story of the Ferntree Gully office has been quite phenomenal. 

Not only has the office enjoyed a tremendous record over a long period, but many of our Sales and Rental staff have achieved outstanding results over the same time.  Paul Stone and Tom Tsiagalos have both established themselves within this “service hungry” industry with outstanding results over an extended period.

per
name: Stockdale & Leggo Ferntree Gully

description: Within our area it is essential for us to have personnel from a variety of cultures. Our team can speak most languages & it is a decided advantage for buyers to be able to communicate with our consultants. Our Dynamic Team is the most extensive & successful network in metropolitan Melbourne. Our local Monash network incorporates our Glen Waverley and Mount Waverley offices. We are your local agents - we live & work here, we appreciate the lifestyle benefits & advantages of living in this area from great school to parks, transport to restaurants. There are not many other areas as perfect as these for 'the dream lifestyle'
name: Barry Plant Monash

address1: Shop L01, P01A Parkmore Shopping Centre
description:
Our commitment is to ADVISE, HELP & CARE FOR YOU. 

We will provide you with the utmost care, consideration, ethics & honesty as your real estate agent of choice.

The successful sale and purchase of your home, investment or development is usually the single most important transaction you will make in your life, and is therefore high up on the list of potentially stressful situations.

Good communication on our part will help reduce these stresses and make your sale go through smoothly and efficiently and hopefully bring you, your family and friends back to us for your future property needs.

We will be here to help guide you through every step of your real estate journey.

Whether it is to find you your first home, investment or development site, we will be here to liaise with the wide range of people including solicitors, plumbers, cleaners, gardeners and builders to ensure that everything runs smoothly so you need have no concerns.

At Raine & Horne Keysborough we will give you three times the level of service, we will provide you with an experienced & qualified team with three times the levels of enthusiasm, commitment and support which you may not have experienced before, in order for you to achieve the finest real estate experience which will keep you coming back to us again and again and again.
name: Sovereign Properties

description:
The team at Schroeder & Wallis are real estate experts within the City of Knox. We offer an unmatched level of service to all our clients no matter what your property requirements are.

 

What makes us unique is the proactive nature of our entire approach to servicing your property needs. We wear our passion for real estate on our sleeve and constantly assess and reassess the effectiveness of our campaigns with a view to improving and embracing innovation and creative thinking to guarantee outstanding results. We are highly analytical, anticipating individual needs and applying our market insights to deliver the best result for people buying, selling or leasing property.

 

The service we provide at Schroeder & Wallis is defined by passion and integrity. Combining award-winning, large-scale thinking with a commitment to tailored client care we strive to exceed expectations at all times. Above all else, our service is effective. Our specialist expertise, market knowledge and impeccable attention to detail achieve strong returns for our steady client base.
name: Schroeder & Wallis

description:
Grandstand Real Estate has been established since 2015. As an independent real estate agency, Grandstand has been servicing all areas of Melbourne. Since its establishment, Grandstand has successfully leased and/or sold properties in Melbourne sought after locations including Burwood, Camberwell, Doncaster, Ferntree Gully, Glen Waverley, Kew, Knoxfield, Malvern, Melbourne CBD, Mitcham, Mount Waverley, Ringwood, Rowville, Scoresby, South Yarra, Wantirna, Wantirna South, Wheelers Hill and so on.

We are a dynamic and multi-cultural team that strives to achieve grand outcomes for our clients with dedication and integrity. With a CLIENT-CENTRIC approach in everything we do, we actively listen to our clients’ needs, carefully plan and organize our tasks, and effectively carry out actions to deliver the best outcomes for our clients.

Conan Ong, the director of Grandstand, has more than 25 years of real estate experience. As director, Conan believes in leading by example. His career history can be measured by literally hundreds of property transactions, many of which have delivered outcomes to his clients far above their expectations. We STAND with our clients for GRAND outcomes. Together we GRAND, together we STAND.
name: Grandstand Real Estate

description:
Lawson Real Estate was established in 1990 by Steven Lawson as a specialist Industrial Commercial Retail agency with emphasis on serving the Eastern and South Eastern market.

Conveniently located in Mount Waverley, our office is within minutes to most industrial areas having immediate access to the South Eastern Freeway and major North South arterial roads.

Lawson Real Estate Pty Ltd has grown to be a recognised force in this specialised market providing Sales, Leasing, Property Management and Consulting services.

Our extensive computerised systems, include both property management and our unique Listings/Sales database with in excess of 5,500 individual property details, this enables our office to undertake extensive direct marketing and have access to detailed property information unavailable to others.

A major difference and advantage that our office has over many agencies is that we place great importance on teamwork within the office, ensuring that all information and potential opportunities are maximised
name: Lawson Real Estate

description:
Love Commercial represents the natural expansion of the family run Love Real Estate residential network founded in 1945 by Mr E J Love.

The original office of Love Real Estate was established in the newly created Melbourne suburb of Reservoir, and with the rapid growth since then of Melbourne City to the North, Love Real Estate now has an additional 6 offices located in Thornbury, Preston, Thomastown, Mill Park and Epping.

With the further construction of Melbourne’s Western Ring Road and CityLink, and the resulting development of extensive commercial and industrial facilities to maximise predominantly transport and logistical benefits to business, John Love identified an opportunity to capitalise on the increase in demand for the sale and management of commercial and industrial properties in the region.

Based upon this business opportunity, Love Commercial was established in 1997 and now offers a specialist service in Commercial and Industrial Real Estate from Footscray in Melbourne’s west, around the city’s northern fringe, to the Dandenong ranges in Melbourne’s east. A second office in Bayswater supports Love Commercial’s Headquarters in Reservoir. 

Love Commercial provides specialist services and professional advice regarding complex Commercial and Industrial Real Estate issues such as:


• The Goods and Services Tax (GST)
• Retail Tenancies Legislation
• Depreciation along with more complex building information and management systems
• Sales/Auctions/Leasing
• Property Management
• Certified Valuations etc

The team at Love Commercial prides itself on delivering specialist service and advice that is not only reliable, accurate and cost efficient, but most importantly, reflects an extensive knowledge of local market conditions.
name: Love Commercial

description:
Rowville's dynamic team in sales and rentals, linked with the neighbouring Barry Plant offices offers a powerful network achieving excellent results. Whether you are buying, selling or renting a home we are at your service. 

Since it's inception Barry Plant– Rowville has strived to build a professional and reputable real estate business. We pride ourselves on the reputation that we have developed.

Our aim is - 'To be professional and to provide a caring team of people who will work for you – our customer, to reach our common goal of successfully marketing real estate.'
name: Barry Plant Rowville

description:
Welcome to LJ Hooker Rowville. 

We have multiple offices currently working together under the same diverse management team in different areas, with a combined over 40 plus years of experience in all aspects of real estate.

Whether you are looking to sell your property, purchase an investment property or perhaps looking for an experienced and dedicated Property Manager to manage your rental property. Our objective is to provide our clients with a real estate experience second to none.
name: LJ Hooker Rowville

description:
At Ray White Rowville we work harder for our customers.

Backed with over 116 years of experience from Australasia’s largest real estate group, Ray White Rowville clients can rest assured that they have selected the right team.

Having established themselves as market leaders in the Knox area, we know firsthand what makes the area and the lifestyle attractive. What’s more, we know what motivates buyers in the local market.

Our comprehensive past client and buyer database ensures that your property is presented to more genuine buyers, to maximise the competition to buy your property. During the campaign, we use a refined set of processes that have been specifically designed to get you the best possible price for your property.

When you choose an agent at Ray White Rowville, you get the support of our full team. Our unique structure encourages all agents to work together to achieve the best price for your property. With over 1,000 offices across 11 countries, we can also connect you to buyers from all over the world. This international exposure is an added dimension no other agency can rival.

We pride ourselves on providing an exceptional level of personal and professional service to make the selling process easy and rewarding for all our clients.
name: Ray White Rowville

description:
THE BEST REAL ESTATE RESULT... GUARANTEED              

Buying, Selling, Renting.

M J Docking & Associates is geared towards achieving the maximum price for your property.

M J Docking & Associates are only as good as our last sale and we will strive to make you another spokesperson for our service.

Visit Our Offices at:

606 Canterbury Road, Vermont
Ph: (03) 8877 7022
FAX: (03) 8877 7062

Established 1983 by Max Docking, a local resident since 1956, M J Docking & Associates’ knowledge of Vermont, Vermont South and its surrounding suburbs is second to none. Our unique insight into the district is of great benefit to both vendors and purchasers who are looking for the true atmosphere of the local area

Experience is why we're the largest in the area . . .  Attitude is why we're the best!
name: M.J Docking & Associates

description:
Welcome to First National Real Estate Quinta

We’re dedicated to delivering an exceptional experience from our Vermont South office, so every member of our team strives to make a difference. That begins with our promise – We put you first.

When you need real estate services, it’s hard to beat a brand that has been independently verified as having Australia’s happiest clients but that’s us, so relax.

To find out how real estate agents are rated across Australia, IPSOS surveyed Australian adults in 2016 (and Colmar Brunton in 2016 and 2017) who had employed an agent in their area in recent years, whether it related to the buying or selling of a property, lease management or renting.

IPSOS found Australians say First National agents ‘make buying and selling easy’ and that ‘they do what they say they will do’. Colman Brunton rated First National agents above other agents in every category measured, including communication and advice, problem resolution, contract handling, marketing, moving services and value for money.

So, whether you’re looking to rent, buy or sell a property in the Vermont South, Vermont, Burwood East, Knoxfield or Nunawading areas, our team will help you find the perfect place.

We put you first.

We Sell For: People that are Downsizing, those getting Divorced, people who have to sell because of Debt, Power of Attorney needing to sell because of Death in the family or those who simply Desire to make money out of their property transaction.

Regards,

Trevor Pickens

Director
name: First National Quinta

description: In an increasingly fast-paced world, we know that while people want the most professional efficient service, they still prize the fundamentals of honesty and integrity from real estate consultants committed to achieving their clients’ goals. That’s why at Harcourts we combine world-renowned technology, training and systems with a focus on establishing trust and respect with our clients who always remain at the centre of the process. Whether you’re buying or selling residential, commercial, rural, lifestyle, holiday rentals, land, or a new home, at Harcourts we’re proud to say we put the focus on Global. National. Local. and most importantly, You.
name: Harcourts Vermont South

description:
Providing Solutions & Satisfaction to your needs
Speak to anyone who has experienced the PROCESS of buying or selling Real Estate and often their findings are a combination of stress, disappointment and ultimately compromise! One of the many goals of K R Peters Pty Ltd - Wantirna South is to ensure your next move is a positive one.

K R Peters Pty Ltd - Wantirna South was founded around one simple mission. 

"To deliver RESULTS that exceed our clients EXPECTATIONS". 

We have created 'Best Practice Systems' that provide solutions and satisfaction to your most desired wants and needs. At the foundation of our 'success system' is a philosophical shift from being a 'facilitator' presenting to a Real Estate Consumer to becoming a 'catalyst' for a Real Estate Client to find success in an industry that for decades has been inefficient and often ineffective.

"Disappointment is the difference between what a client EXPECTS and what the agent DELIVERS"

K R Peters Pty Ltd - Wantirna South has thoroughly researched what a client requires from their agent. What they have told us is that they are craving a 'professional' who can 'listen' to their individual wants and needs and provide solutions for them!

K R Peters Pty Ltd - Wantirna South is that professional!
name: KR Peters Wantirna South

description: If you're looking to put your home on the market for any reason, come to the professionals who will provide you with the highest level of client service - something you should not hope for, but expect when making such a decision. Our team here at OBrien Real Estate Wantirna will deliver top-tier professional property solutions right across the board, whether you're buying, selling, renting or leasing.
name: OBrien Real Estate Wantirna

description:
Roger Davis Pty Ltd was established in 1971 and remains an independent family business.

OUR SALES TEAM

The skilled and expert sales team at Roger Davis offers our clients a unique selling experience where you are sure to find our service to be both professional and limitless:

We understand how important your home is to you and every listing is given personalised attention.

We work with you to ensure an effective advertising campaign is created to specifically suit your property and budget. We advertise on four Web sites as well as our own web site. We advertise each week in the local Leader newspaper being the Waverley Gazette and can produce for you quality boards and brochures.

There are no language barriers when you choose Roger Davis Pty Ltd our staff speak a range of different languages including:

  • Madarin
  • Cantonese
  • Hok Kien
  • Teo Chiev
  • Vietnamese
  • Cambodian
  • Greek

WE HAVE A STRONG SALES TEAM THAT ACHIEVES AMAZING RESULTS

The Rental Department

Is lead by a team of enthusiastic, dedicated senior property managers, our rental department has continued to grow and become one of the largest and most pro-active rental departments in Waverley.

Our Company is confident in managing residential, commercial and rural properties all over Melbourne. We take property management seriously and we provide our clients with expertise in all aspects of rental management.

Property Management is a major part of our business and we take great pride in our high standard of personalised service to our Landlords and Tenants. Regular training ensures our Department has a sharp knowledge of the current rental market.

The Goodwill created over the years where Tenants ultimately become Landlords is the basis for a lot of our business.

When associating with our family Agency, you can be assured of an efficient and professional service.
name: Roger Davis Real Estate

description:
Ethical. Hardworking. Honest.

These three principles are not to be taken lightly and is well understood by founders Kenneth Kong and Kenneth Ooi who endeavour to integrate them into every aspect of their business in order to provide an exceptional real estate experience.

Inspired by the bellmen who work tirelessly greeting you at the grand hotel entrance with hospitality and grace, Bellman Real Estate is here to serve you.

With a combined experience of over 30 years, you can trust in their highly qualified team of advisors and negotiators.

Bellman Real Estate stays true to its principles; giving an authentic experience that utilises a unique approach to each client, and above all, respects you and your wished by providing first class services, guiding you into the next chapter. Whether it be selling or managing one of your most valuable assets. 

With a personalised and bespoke approach, Bellman Real Estate is looking forward to opening more doors for you, allowing you to live life to the fullest and spend time with those who matter most. 

Bellman, at your service.
name: Bellman Real Estate

description: Sales and marketing experts in new and existing residential property.
name: CRH Property

description:
Boronia is one of the many suburbs to be found in the 'the most liveable City' – Knox. A vibrant and modern area nestled against the picturesque backdrop of the Dandenong Ranges. The Boronia area continues to build on its strengths of community, business and commitment to the environment.

Boronia boasts an array of lifestyle opportunities for you and your families, including a choice of excellent private and government schools, a tertiary college, reliable public transport and the second largest shopping centre in Australia, Knox City.

With over 350 specialty stores, Knox City together with Knox Ozone provides a unique shopping, entertainment, leisure and dining experience.

Mark Schroeder and the team at Barry Plant Boronia provide a marketing edge to vendors by placing their properties before more buyers everyday. They do this by tapping into the Melbourne wide Barry Plant network which includes working closely with the neighbouring offices of Rowville and Wantirna.

At Barry Plant Boronia, we feel that being entrusted to help sell or purchase your greatest financial asset is a huge privilege and responsibility. Therefore, our ultimate aim is to make the whole experience of buying or selling real estate as enjoyable and stress free as possible every time. Occasionally someone experiences a stress free home sale by accident. We’re here to make it happen on purpose.

Boronia's dynamic teamwork, negotiation skills and their high standards of personal client attention make them the strongest force in the Knox area.

"What lies before us and what lies beyond us is tiny compared to what lies within us – It's not just another property.....It's your home and we'll treat it that way"
name: Barry Plant Boronia

description:
iTRAK is moving you with the times......

iTRAK Real Estate was born from a need to offer Home Sellers a far more relevant service, one that is in line with modern technology. We provide the most efficient way to sell your home.

Our efficiency stems from an understanding of modern buyer research behavior which translates into a business model that keeps overheads and costs low

The internet has been the most powerful change to the real estate industry ever. It's changed the way buyers search for properties. It also has resulted in a massive change to just how much competition Home Sellers can attract on their home. Using a smart and professional sales strategy a well presented home can generate upwards of 100 buyer inspections in the first two weeks.

Founding Director David Stewart has established a team of like minded and experienced Agents;who can offer Home Sellers professional guidance and strategies to generate a Premium Price with the benefit of saving money. iTRAK is proud of the difference we are already making for so many Home Sellers; having already sold homes in over 50 Melbourne suburbs. We look forward to speaking to you any time; whether selling your home or taking care of your investment property.
name: Biggin & Scott Boronia

address2: Cnr Burwood Hwy & Ferntree Gully Rd
description:
Our office was established in Ferntree Gully in mid 1970’s when the local area was expanding in leaps and bounds. The farmland was being developed into housing estates with allotments ranging from 750sqm to 1000sqm. As the population grew, businesses grew to meet the population’s demands. 1980 – 1990 was the growth decade in both residential, commercial and industrial when Ferntree Gully and the Knox area as a whole was transformed into a more modern and vibrant area.

 

Abley Real Estate joined the Professionals Real Estate Group as one of their first members’s well over 30 years ago as it was 100% Australian owned and operated. Today the group has well over 300 offices and has expanded to New Zealand, throughout South East Asia area and now looking to the United State of America. The group prides itself on its social responsibility through office contribution at local and national levels, as a key supporter to the National Breast Cancer Foundation and the Child Cancer Foundation.

 

Ray Abley is also renowned for his generosity to local sporting and community groups for junior sports for nearly 30 years.

 

Abley Real Estate Pty Ltd is known for the stability of their staff when most senior staff has been established for 15 – 20 years.

 

The office have specialised staff in the following categories.

a)            Residential Sales

b)            Residential Property Management

c)            Commercial Industrial Leasing & Sales

d)            Project Management in developments and constructions

e)            Buyers advocate service

 

You can feel confident when you appoint Abley Real Estate Pty Ltd to handle all your property needs because we have the necessary experienced staff with a minimum of 15 years experience. Our office has been voted Number One Real Estate Agency of the year in Knox on a number of occasions.
name: Abley Real Estate Pty Ltd

description:
Ray White Real Estate Ferntree Gully

Ray White Ferntree Gully enjoys a high community profile with an excellent position on Ferntree Gully Road next door to Fernwood Gym.
At Ray White Ferntree Gully we work as a team to offer maximum coverage to our clients in the sale & management of their property, enabling us to achieve excellent results for our landlords and top prices for our vendors. 
We believe that solid and ethical work practices based on continual communication with our clients is the only way to work. Much of our business comes from referrals as we aim to build our business and provide a complete Real Estate Service with honesty and integrity at its foundation.
name: Ray White Ferntree Gully

description:
Stockdale & Leggo Ferntree Gully is a leading member of the Stockdale & Leggo franchise group, Victoria’s largest, consisting of approximately 80 offices state-wide.  The Stockdale & Leggo group has been delivering real estate services to the people of Victoria for over 75 years, beginning from a single office in Glenhuntly around 1934.

The Ferntree Gully office,  as you now see it, began in 1996.  Under the careful eye of Paul Stone, Director and Tom Tsiagalos, Sales Manager, the office has grown into the market leader it is today.  The business offers “everything real estate” from Sales and Auctions to Property Management for both Residential and Commercial properties. 

Currently employing dedicated staff, the Ferntree Gully office includes a Sales Team actively listing and selling property, Residential Property Managers and a very professional team of Administration staff providing behind-the-scenes support.

Under the management of Tom Tsiagalos, his team is making its mark within this high traffic location.  With thousands of people per week visiting the Mountain Gate Shopping Centre and frontage to Burwood Highway, the exposure has provided an even greater profile for the business and more importantly our vendors.The success story of the Ferntree Gully office has been quite phenomenal. 

Not only has the office enjoyed a tremendous record over a long period, but many of our Sales and Rental staff have achieved outstanding results over the same time.  Paul Stone and Tom Tsiagalos have both established themselves within this “service hungry” industry with outstanding results over an extended period.

per
name: Stockdale & Leggo Ferntree Gully

description:
The team at Schroeder & Wallis are real estate experts within the City of Knox. We offer an unmatched level of service to all our clients no matter what your property requirements are.

 

What makes us unique is the proactive nature of our entire approach to servicing your property needs. We wear our passion for real estate on our sleeve and constantly assess and reassess the effectiveness of our campaigns with a view to improving and embracing innovation and creative thinking to guarantee outstanding results. We are highly analytical, anticipating individual needs and applying our market insights to deliver the best result for people buying, selling or leasing property.

 

The service we provide at Schroeder & Wallis is defined by passion and integrity. Combining award-winning, large-scale thinking with a commitment to tailored client care we strive to exceed expectations at all times. Above all else, our service is effective. Our specialist expertise, market knowledge and impeccable attention to detail achieve strong returns for our steady client base.
name: Schroeder & Wallis

description:
Lawson Real Estate was established in 1990 by Steven Lawson as a specialist Industrial Commercial Retail agency with emphasis on serving the Eastern and South Eastern market.

Conveniently located in Mount Waverley, our office is within minutes to most industrial areas having immediate access to the South Eastern Freeway and major North South arterial roads.

Lawson Real Estate Pty Ltd has grown to be a recognised force in this specialised market providing Sales, Leasing, Property Management and Consulting services.

Our extensive computerised systems, include both property management and our unique Listings/Sales database with in excess of 5,500 individual property details, this enables our office to undertake extensive direct marketing and have access to detailed property information unavailable to others.

A major difference and advantage that our office has over many agencies is that we place great importance on teamwork within the office, ensuring that all information and potential opportunities are maximised
name: Lawson Real Estate

description:
For over half a century, Crabtrees Real Estate have been providing Melbourne with a service built on constant success and proven experience. It’s no wonder we are regarded as one of Melbourne’s best commercial and industrial specialists. Complete property management that takes the day-to-day hassle away from you, so you can sit back and watch your investment grow from strength to strength.

When it comes to understanding the market, our broad network and solid ties with the south-eastern suburbs means our clients always get results way above their expectation. From leasing to management, all our staff are passionate about real estate, providing a professional and competitive service for all your Commercial and Industrial needs.
name: Crabtrees Real Estate Oakleigh

description:
Rowville's dynamic team in sales and rentals, linked with the neighbouring Barry Plant offices offers a powerful network achieving excellent results. Whether you are buying, selling or renting a home we are at your service. 

Since it's inception Barry Plant– Rowville has strived to build a professional and reputable real estate business. We pride ourselves on the reputation that we have developed.

Our aim is - 'To be professional and to provide a caring team of people who will work for you – our customer, to reach our common goal of successfully marketing real estate.'
name: Barry Plant Rowville

description:
Positioned in the new Corner development at Wellington Village Shopping Centre, Harcourts Rowville offers a fresh and dynamic approach to real estate.

In an increasingly fast-paced world, Harcourts Rowville knows that while people want a professional and efficient service, they still prize the fundamentals of honesty and integrity from real estate consultants committed to achieving their clients’ goals.

That’s why Harcourts Rowville combines world-renowned technology, training and systems with a focus on establishing trust and respect with their clients who always remain at the centre of the process.

Whether you’re buying, selling or renting residential property, Harcourts Rowville is proud to offer a service which continually delivers superior results and exceeds client expectations.


Harcourts Rowville's Values:

  • People First
  • Doing the right thing
  • Being courageous
  • Fun and Laughter
name: Harcourts Rowville

description:
Welcome to LJ Hooker Rowville. 

We have multiple offices currently working together under the same diverse management team in different areas, with a combined over 40 plus years of experience in all aspects of real estate.

Whether you are looking to sell your property, purchase an investment property or perhaps looking for an experienced and dedicated Property Manager to manage your rental property. Our objective is to provide our clients with a real estate experience second to none.
name: LJ Hooker Rowville

description:
At Ray White Rowville we work harder for our customers.

Backed with over 116 years of experience from Australasia’s largest real estate group, Ray White Rowville clients can rest assured that they have selected the right team.

Having established themselves as market leaders in the Knox area, we know firsthand what makes the area and the lifestyle attractive. What’s more, we know what motivates buyers in the local market.

Our comprehensive past client and buyer database ensures that your property is presented to more genuine buyers, to maximise the competition to buy your property. During the campaign, we use a refined set of processes that have been specifically designed to get you the best possible price for your property.

When you choose an agent at Ray White Rowville, you get the support of our full team. Our unique structure encourages all agents to work together to achieve the best price for your property. With over 1,000 offices across 11 countries, we can also connect you to buyers from all over the world. This international exposure is an added dimension no other agency can rival.

We pride ourselves on providing an exceptional level of personal and professional service to make the selling process easy and rewarding for all our clients.
name: Ray White Rowville

description:
Welcome to First National Real Estate Quinta

We’re dedicated to delivering an exceptional experience from our Vermont South office, so every member of our team strives to make a difference. That begins with our promise – We put you first.

When you need real estate services, it’s hard to beat a brand that has been independently verified as having Australia’s happiest clients but that’s us, so relax.

To find out how real estate agents are rated across Australia, IPSOS surveyed Australian adults in 2016 (and Colmar Brunton in 2016 and 2017) who had employed an agent in their area in recent years, whether it related to the buying or selling of a property, lease management or renting.

IPSOS found Australians say First National agents ‘make buying and selling easy’ and that ‘they do what they say they will do’. Colman Brunton rated First National agents above other agents in every category measured, including communication and advice, problem resolution, contract handling, marketing, moving services and value for money.

So, whether you’re looking to rent, buy or sell a property in the Vermont South, Vermont, Burwood East, Knoxfield or Nunawading areas, our team will help you find the perfect place.

We put you first.

We Sell For: People that are Downsizing, those getting Divorced, people who have to sell because of Debt, Power of Attorney needing to sell because of Death in the family or those who simply Desire to make money out of their property transaction.

Regards,

Trevor Pickens

Director
name: First National Quinta

description:
Wantirna is one of the many suburbs to be found in the 'the most liveable City' – Knox. A vibrant and modern area nestled against the picturesque backdrop of the Dandenong Ranges. The Wantirna area continues to build on its strengths of community, business and commitment to the environment. Wantirna boasts an array of lifestyle opportunities for you and your families, including a choice of excellent private and government schools, a tertiary college, reliable public transport and the second largest shopping centre in Australia, Knox City. With over 350 specialty stores, Knox City together with Knox Ozone provides a unique shopping, entertainment, leisure and dining experience.

Brendan Murphy, Adam Sorrell and the team at Barry Plant Wantirna provide a marketing edge to vendors by placing their properties before more buyers everyday. They do this by tapping into the Melbourne wide Barry Plant network which includes working closely with the neighbouring offices of Rowville and Boronia. At Barry Plant Wantirna, we feel that being entrusted to help sell or purchase your greatest financial asset is a huge privilege and responsibility. Therefore, our ultimate aim is to make the whole experience of buying or selling real estate as enjoyable and stress free as possible every time. Occasionally someone experiences a stress free home sale by accident. We’re here to make it happen on purpose. Wantirna's dynamic teamwork, negotiation skills and their high standards of personal client attention make them the strongest force in the Knox area. "What lies before us and what lies beyond us is tiny compared to what lies within us – It's not just another property....It's your home and we’ll treat it that way"
name: Barry Plant Wantirna

description:
Cameron. is a successful and dominant company with a fine reputation and a strong team of sales, leasing and administration staff dedicated to producing outstanding results.

The cornerstone of our success has been our comprehensive knowledge and commitment to the South East Industrial/Commercial market. This knowledge developed over 40 years of hands on, on the ground dedication to a specific market place has given us the edge over national and local based competition.

Cameron. services our large base of clients from two offices based in Dandenong South and Wantirna.
name: Cameron - Eastern Office

description:
First National Real Estate Wantirna is the real estate specialist for Wantirna, Knoxfield, Wantirna South, Bayswater and surrounds. Providing real estate services ranging from residential sales, property management to commercial real estate sales and lease, First National Real Estate Wantirna can help you with all your real estate needs.

At First National Real Estate Wantirna, you will always be treated as our top priority. At First National Real Estate Wantirna – we put you first.
name: First National Real Estate Wantirna

description:
We are a progressive family owned real estate agency offering a genuinely personal level of service, while at the same time delivering the highest standard of professional real estate service and expertise.  Our company focus is on residential property management services and real estate sales within the City of Knox and surrounding Melbourne suburbs.  Our success as an ‘independent’ real estate agency has been built on the personal referral of business from past satisfied clients, tenants and landlords together with our outstanding reputation and local knowledge.

Hill Real Estate and all Hill Real Estate staff are members of the Real Estate Institute of Victoria and has suitably qualified and professionally motivated employees to enable us to guarantee a constantly high standard of personal real estate service. Our office is conveniently located on Burwood Highway, in the white terraces opposite Knox City Shopping Centre.
name: Hill Real Estate

description:
Experienced and strong performing in any market, Professionals Wantirna are highly regarded for their tenacity in achieving premium results and conscientious regard for their clients.

Established in 2001 with a commitment to excellence, Professionals Wantirna have a reputation as top performers in sales, projects, auctions, property leasing and management. We love what we do and we do it with passion, drive, excellence and enthusiasm. Referrals and repeat business from happy clients are keys to our success.

Working together as part of a 300 office network with a multi-lingual team, we employ marketing strategies that connect with people locally and internationally. We are invested in building authentic relationships with clients at every price point.

We know Knox. Our families grew up here and we view the eastern suburbs as the most liveable and desirable. We are proud to support the local community by assisting with school functions, sporting events, fetes, fundraisers and donating to the National Breast Cancer Foundation from every sale. As NBCF’s Diamond Partner, Professionals have raised over $3,000,000 and counting.

Our determination to remain customer focused is supported by our attention to detail, unrivalled knowledge, proven marketing strategies, advanced technologies, professionalism and refined negotiating skills to outpace the competition.

Our goal is to create customer happiness and help you achieve your real estate dream.
name: Professionals Wantirna

description:
Ray White Wantirna has established itself as Wantirna’s market leader in quality Real Estate services. Director Zac Clancey and the team of uncompromising Real Estate professionals ensure first class service to all Ray White Wantirna clients.

Ray White Wantirna is strategically located at the Studfield Shopping Centre where several thousand shoppers pass by the window weekly and is consistently a top ten office in the network of over 100 Ray White offices. For obligation free advice whether you are buying, selling, renting or looking to have your investment property professionally managed, call us today.

Our focus is entirely on our clients. We believe that success is built on the strength of the relationships we forge and all of our dedicated agents share our same vision and quest for excellence.

Our services include:

  • Residential sales
  • Residential land sales
  • Residential Rentals

    •
name: Ray White Wantirna

description:
Providing Solutions & Satisfaction to your needs
Speak to anyone who has experienced the PROCESS of buying or selling Real Estate and often their findings are a combination of stress, disappointment and ultimately compromise! One of the many goals of K R Peters Pty Ltd - Wantirna South is to ensure your next move is a positive one.

K R Peters Pty Ltd - Wantirna South was founded around one simple mission. 

"To deliver RESULTS that exceed our clients EXPECTATIONS". 

We have created 'Best Practice Systems' that provide solutions and satisfaction to your most desired wants and needs. At the foundation of our 'success system' is a philosophical shift from being a 'facilitator' presenting to a Real Estate Consumer to becoming a 'catalyst' for a Real Estate Client to find success in an industry that for decades has been inefficient and often ineffective.

"Disappointment is the difference between what a client EXPECTS and what the agent DELIVERS"

K R Peters Pty Ltd - Wantirna South has thoroughly researched what a client requires from their agent. What they have told us is that they are craving a 'professional' who can 'listen' to their individual wants and needs and provide solutions for them!

K R Peters Pty Ltd - Wantirna South is that professional!
name: KR Peters Wantirna South

description: If you're looking to put your home on the market for any reason, come to the professionals who will provide you with the highest level of client service - something you should not hope for, but expect when making such a decision. Our team here at OBrien Real Estate Wantirna will deliver top-tier professional property solutions right across the board, whether you're buying, selling, renting or leasing.
name: OBrien Real Estate Wantirna

description:
Welcome to AgentX Real Estate Berwick 

Welcome to a fresh brand, a fresh philosophy and a fresh way of looking at real estate!

We aim to offer the highest level of customer service matched by our focus on modern communication techniques to take selling your home to the next level. With 100% dedication to each of our individual clients, allow us to come to you and create an experience which is unmatched!

We Can't Hope To Be Different - if we look and sound like all the others!
name: AgentX Real Estate Pty Ltd

description:
Aldrich Homes is a family owned and operated company with family values.
 
 
From traditional detached homes, to home and land packages, townhouses, apartments and more, Aldrich Homes build homes to suit both budget and lifestyle.
 
 If you are looking for outstanding quality and service you can trust then choose Aldrich to bring it all to life.

description:
Our company had its beginning in 1917.  The founder father,  Frank Facey was born in Cranbourne, Victoria and after a career in coach building , started  a Real Estate business in Dandenong.

Frank opened the doors of his Estate Agency in the main street of Dandenong and in 1945 a new site was purchased and a new office built.  In fact, today the current  First National Real Estate Hall & Partners  office is on the same site.

Frank’s son Angus joined his father in the business in 1930.  His son Andrew followed in his footsteps and joined his father in the business in 1968 and took over the management in 1974 .

During the 90’s the group comprised an industrial office in Dandenong as well as residential offices in Dandenong, Berwick, Narre Warren, Endeavour Hills , Mulgrave, Glen Waverley and Pakenham.

The Berwick office combined with Hudson Real Estate Berwick in the late  90’s and in 2002 combined with Cremin Real Estate (Pakenham) .  Both Bill Hudson and Jack Cremin were icons in their  communities.  In recent years the group has consolidated to 3 offices located in  Berwick, Narre Warren  & Pakenham.

Exciting times at First National.  In  July 2011 another change to the business with Andrew Facey our friend and landlord  selling out  and reserving the name Frank Facey for his new development  company.  Our new trading name will be First National Real Estate Neilson Partners with the partnership  across our 3 offices, Narre Warren, Berwick and Pakenham.

Modern technology has been embraced with the computer support linking all residential offices to promote all properties and to support our vendors.  As members of First National we also enjoy the benefit of a 500-office strong referral network throughout Australia and New Zealand.

Today we offer property management across our 3 offices, both residential and commercial as well as sales of all categories of real estate.

Our commitment is long term and to fulfil that our aim is to provide the best in service and results.
name: First National Real Estate Neilson Partners

description:
FROM THE MOUNTAINS TO THE SEA SINCE 1886

Mr Alex Scott established our Company in the then Pioneeering Districts of Gippsland in 1886. Built on a strong foundation of honesty and integrity, our Company today continues to enjoy a long association with generations of loyal clients.



From 1931 the Company was managed by the son of Alex Scott, Stewart Scott. Stewart Scott worked tirelessly for his Industry. He loved Gippsland and the people he met in his job. This earned him strong respect from his staff and clients. Stewart remained at the helm and steadily guided and saw the expansion of the Company to proudly celebrate its Centenary in 1986. Stewarts motto "Success Through Service" has served the company well. 



In 1950 Bruce Gibson, a grandson of Alex Scott, was introduced to ultimately assume a greater amount of the responsibility. Bruce Gibson became the third generation of the family to have the responsibility of Company Manager on the death of Stewart in 1988. 



In 1993 Alex Scott & Staff was formed, providing Staff the opportunity of acquiring a shareholding and to form a Board of Directors with Bruce Gibson remaining as Chairman. This board of family and staff shareholders has overseen a further expansion of the Company, particularly in relation to the Real Estate Division, which combined with the extensive and long established Livestock interests provides a most vibrant and well informed Agency. description:
Choosing An Agency Is Tough... LetUs Convince You!

1. Save Up To 65% on Agent’s Fees

We believe the industry must accept a change in the way salespeople operate being an industry leader, Changing Places have introduced a “Fixed Fee” commission structure based on the general demographic of the buyer, and the level of effort and resources required to achieve the best possible outcome for our clients, not the dollar value of your property. Our unique business model allows us to reduce running costs without sacrificing our world-class service, therefore we choose to pass this saving onto our clients saving you up to 65% on typical agent’s fees.

2. Our Centralised Database

We are in constant communication with a vast number of qualified buyers each week. These buyers are entered into our centralized data management system can opt in to automatically advised of any new property listings that match their buying criteria. Unlike traditional agency networks, all of our Area Specialists have access to this national network of buyers, effectively allowing our salespeople to market your property on a national scale putting your property in front of more buyers each week.

More Buyers + Emotionally Connected + In Competition = Premium Price

3. Our National Network of Salespeople

We employ, train and support a National network of salespeople who are experts in their field and well networked within their territory. Our training is intense so we ensure each and every Area Specialist is fully equipped and capable to effectively manage the sale of your property.

4. Our Website

In today’s world over 85% of real estate business happens online. We provide a modern platform for buyers and sellers alike to obtain up-to-date information about the property market, industry trends and tips on buying and selling residential real estate. We are continually striving to push the limits of technology.

5. A Tailored Approach

We do not favour one sale method over another. The most effective method of sale can vary from suburb to suburb, state to state. It is our approach to act in the best interest of our clients and in too many cases a property is auctioned only to leave an owner ultimately disappointed. Our Experienced Area Specialists have an intimate knowledge of their marketplace and will submit their recommendations based on factual evidence and the individual needs of the property. Fact: Out of area and passive buyers are more likely to pay a premium price for a property!

6. Personal Service

In most real estate agencies, you start out with the Principal of the firm or a Senior Salesperson, however, you ultimately find the person who ends up handing your sale is far less experienced. With Changing Places, the Area Specialist is dedicated to your property from day one and stays with you right throughout the sale process.

7. Administration Support

By providing exceptional administration support to all of our Area Specialists we eliminate a large percentage of downtime allowing our salespeople to focus the majority of their energy on achieving the best result for our clients, spending more time working with potential buyers for your property.

8. Training & Development

We believe training is key to success – all our salespeople go through an initial induction program into our brand were we teach demonstrate how our unique philosophy and commission structure can help everyday sellers who are looking for a great real estate experience. In addition to this we provide access to ongoing training events and seminars to ensure our team are fully equipped with state-of-the-art tools, knowledge, and industry best practices ensuring the very best possible outcome can be achieved for our clients.
name: Changing Places Real Estate Consultants

description:
What’s in a name? Elite is the word that guides the culture at Elite Women Real Estate (EWRE). The essential capabilities required to become a good real estate agent are strong active network connections, professional competency, firm negotiation services and familiarity with the economic variables that affect suburbs. The name EWRE means superior skills and culture.

EWRE embraces the superior values of equity and fairness and those tenets are reflected in every transaction. Nurturing skills requires a work culture that is safe to drive efficiency and effectiveness. When people are free to focus on work and are not distracted with negativity, productivity increases. Extensively reported toxic workplaces illustrates clearly the cost to business and as we celebrate International Women’s Day, EWRE reflects that safe work culture. As ‘necessity is the mother of invention’ the need for change is here.

Real estate was originally male dominated and practitioners did not fully address the needs of women other than the stereotypical functional aspects of the property. Today, women are independent decision makers and investors with interests that far exceed traditional roles. As women entered the profession the fundamentals were retained however women added diversity and representation.

EWRE agents are the property relationship builders because women champion relationships. The resources within a location, the growth of the area, the development potential, migratory behaviours and the myriad of other associations are what EWRE capitalises on for buyers and sellers. Utilising local knowledge, macro fundamentals and an e-commerce platform makes EWRE a cost-effective disrupter.

The distinctive skill set that EWRE agents offer, is derived from the inherent understanding of 52% of the population -women - clearly a point of difference. EWRE aims to service all real estate consumers and recognises the property relationship building elements that are needed. From home ownership to income supplementation and retirement planning the future of the real estate industry requires outstanding service and knowledge and that is what is in the name EWRE.
name: EWRE, Servicing Victoria and Queensland Australia

description:
Finning & Company Pty. Ltd. was first established in 1952 under the name of "Cranbourne Real Estate and Business Agency" by the late Mr. Jack Finning and Mrs. Lorraine Finning and it is now one the most prominent and active real estate agencys in the District.

In 1982 the company became a founding member of the First National Group of Estate Agents and as a co-operative of independent agencies, this group now has more than 450 offices throughout Australia and New Zealand. This association has enabled the company to offer a strong referral network and relocation service to it's clients for over 30 years.

In September 1986, the company relocated to its newly constructed offices at 148 High Street, on the corner of Stawell Street, thereby providing it with a distinctive and high profile location from which to conduct its business. Since that time the company has operated under the trading name of Finning First National Real Estate.

As innovators within the real estate industry with a stable & active team constantly on the lookout for new ideas, our Company continued its role as a market leader as we eagerly expanded our market share within the Cranbourne area.

For more than 30 years we have offered our clients and customers a comprehensive 7 day a week trading policy and in 1996 we extended our office closing time until late each week. In addition, our main business telephone number is contactable 24 hours per day to ensure that we are available whenever our clients need us. Operating 7 days a week with one of the most experienced sales teams in Cranbourne, we have more contact with buyers and command a larger portion of the sales market than any other agency in the area. 

Our high profile, well located office, bright & prominent window display and highly competent and professional Sales and Property Management Departments are second to none within the modern real estate industry. With a commitment to on-going training, up to date modern technology and continuous professional development for all of our staff, we are able to ensure that our skills, tools and knowledge of the industry are always right up to the mark.

We have served Cranbourne & the surrounding areas for over 65 Years now & our entire Company philosophy has and always will be "Client Benefit Based" to ensure that we always deliver a standard of real estate service which our clients will remember for all of the right reasons.

Hard work, solid training and ethical dealings with clients have enabled Finning First National to win & receive numerous industry awards for both the office and individual Sales people over the years reinforcing that we are on track with our clients needs.

In July 2016 First National Finning achieved another milestone with a change of ownership to three current staff members, Dean Tucker, Rick Lauretta, Jason Brown & John Lauretta to steer the company on to its next generation of community service and yet maintain its family connection to John & Lorraine Tucker & the founders of the modern day company.

With over forty years of experience at Finnings between Rick, Dean & Jason in a range of roles throughout the company from Residential, commercial & rural - lifestyle sales to administration management they are well versed in the complex procedures undertaken. Johns background in building, construction & property development brings in another facet to the wide range of skills now available to the staff & clients of First National Finnings.

With the introduction of new, exciting and up to the minute technology advances in the Real Estate industry & the adherence to the outstanding client care and company history, everyone who serves at Finnings recognises this as one of our most in demand strengths we are well situated to move and develop First National Finnings into the future.
name: Finning First National

We are residential real estate specialists and have been selling residential real estate since 1999 and have gained a vast amount of knowledge and experience in that time.

Whether you choose to sell your property by Private Treaty or Auction we can help you achieve the highest possible price. There is no extra charge to sell by Auction.

Our commission structure is such that it will save you money when compared to the standard industry commission and at the same time it provides an incentive to achieve the highest possible price for your property.

Our marketing packages are property focused and not agent focused, the idea is to promote your property and not the individual sales agent.

We do not offer gimmicks or other inducements, but, we do offer a personal service that will treat you as a valued client rather than just another number.

Being 'hands on' Directors, Michelle & James are genuinely committed to getting you the highest price and saving you money- "The Way Real Estate Should Be"
name: Munn Partners Real Estate

description:
Ray White Carrum Downs Know How to sell your property for more. We work harder for our clients and provide a service second to none. Our experienced agents take the time to understand your needs up front. Ray White continues to be a leader in the real estate industry with our ongoing success in both sales and property management. We have been experts in the local area for over 10 years and now consist of over 20 staff. This unrivalled experience means that we have a better understanding of the property market. Whatever property you’re looking to sell, the Ray White Know How will match it to the right buyer and secure the highest possible price. It’s the reason why we’re Australia’s largest and most experienced real estate group.

Our rentals department is recognised for providing maximum profitability and protection for investors and excellent service to tenants. Our highest priority is client satisfaction. With the introduction of both Peninsula Link and Eastlink, Carrum Downs is fast becoming a popular option for more people with easy access to the city and Mornington Peninsula. Carrum Downs, Skye and Sandhurst offer a wide range of local shopping centres, parks and reserves, restaurants and sporting facilities including; football, soccer, cricket, golf, tennis and lawn bowls. Ray White Carrum Downs enjoys being a part of the local community and are proud sponsors of the Frankston Dolphins Junior Football Club and the Pearcedale Cricket Club.
name: Ray White Carrum Downs

description:
You journey starts with us.

A forward-thinking full-service agency, we embrace new ideas and take an innovative approach to real estate making sure our clients benefit from our expertise and knowledge.
name: Exclusiv Real Estate

description:
Welcome to LJ Hooker Dandenong City.

Our objective is to protect and expand on both the financial and physical wellbeing of your real estate assets and to provide you with the highest level of customer service possible. 

With a team of highly astute negotiators, LJ Hooker Dandenong offers a full range of property services including sales and property management.
name: LJ Hooker Dandenong

description:
Cameron. is a successful and dominant company with a fine reputation and a strong team of sales, leasing and administration staff dedicated to producing outstanding results.

The cornerstone of our success has been our comprehensive knowledge and commitment to the South East Industrial/Commercial market. This knowledge developed over 40 years of hands on, on the ground dedication to a specific market place has given us the edge over national and local based competition.

Cameron. services our large base of clients from two offices based in Dandenong South and Wantirna.
name: Cameron

description:
Our Vision

DB Realty aims to provide outstanding results based on personal and caring customer service. Established in 2004, DB Realty has a short but impressive history as a boutique style agency, renowned for its innovation and integrity.

Our Method

DB Realty offers a hands on approach in maintaining a high level of personalised service the partners are involved in every aspect of the business and they are supported by a friendly and qualifed team committed to customer satisfaction.

This hands on operation guarantees a more effcient business through keeping costs low while making sure that our excellent staff and technical support systems are always in place.

We are a small agency which means that every client is handled with the attention and care they deserve. The team works according to your individual needs combining its extensive real estate knowledge with your own personal vision to ensure that you get the results that are best for you!

Our Promise

At DB Realty we maintain high expectations of ourselves and the products and services we offer.

We are constantly updating our in-house systems to allow for accurate and current information. We also strive to discover new ways to make your experience with us successfully different.

The team at DB Realty will never lose sight of its passion for integrity and exceptional customer service. We aim to do our very best to ensure that our clients are satisfed in achieving paramount results.
name: D B Realty

description:
From its humble beginnings in 1900 Austin Real Estate has proudly stood the test of time and continues its long standing motto – “WE GET RESULTS!”  
The director, Paul Matthews is a Fully Licensed & Accredited Real Estate Agent and has many years of local real estate knowledge. He heads up a modern and professional office located on Nepean Highway providing great exposure for all clientele. Austin Real Estate is staffed by experienced professionals who will assist you in providing the best possible results for all your property needs, whether buying, selling or leasing. To join the ever growing list of satisfied clients, please contact the friendly team at Austin Real Estate. And remember……………………..WE GET RESULTS!!
name: Austin Real Estate

description: Established in 2006 as a premier independent agency servicing the Mornington Peninsula region & Casey municipalities, Eview Group has grown to become a market leader, selling properties in over 100 suburbs across Victoria. Our core values of integrity, trust and honesty are at the forefront of our company's core culture. With aspirations in being a world class leader these values carry across both our residential sales division and our dedicated property management team. Our business is focused on building and improving its strong customer service ethic and developing a 'client for life' relationship with all of our part, current and future clients. With many of the company's staff living locally and staying with the company over numerous years, we consider ourselves a group of enthusiastic, dedicated and passionate locals who heavily involve ourselves in the immediate community. This gives us tremendous insight into the local market - it's previous trends, current movements and future forecasts, giving us one of many reasons why we deliver the best results for our clients!
name: Eview Group - Australia

description:
Welcome to Us Real Estate

Whether you are a buyer or a seller of property, a local resident or a newcomer to our magic city of Frankston, we are here to listen.


Our agency service is rich in integrity and commonsense, high in results and customer satisfaction and low in stress and hassle for our clients. We are professionals of the highest standard.

Our agents are down to earth, hard working, straight talking professionals. Our clients are people who want an honest, no-nonsense service where they have feedback every step of the way as to what we are doing and what prospective buyers are saying. Together it works extremely well.

Marketing

All our properties are photographed professionally to ensure they are marketed in their best light. Our distinctive logo and colour toning, large presence in the Frankston Leader, head turning signs, guaranteed feature property listing on realestate.com.au, listed on domain.com.au, realestateview.com.au, homehound.com.au, yourproperty.com.au, myhome.com.au, our high profile office location and distinctive display window all ensures that we capture the attention of every potential buyer for your property.

Because we are proudly independent agency we don’t have to fit into any corporate template and can design a marketing campaign solely around your property.

As our marketing campaigns are so successful it’s not uncommon to find we have multiple offers on our properties which in turn ensures we achieve the maximum result for our vendors.

And there is more

We have a few more things up our sleeve too. Be sure to ask our Agent when they give you your free appraisal.

Us Real Estate

Where it really is all about U.
name: Us Real Estate

description:
Our company-Melvic, (derived from Melbourne and Victoria,) began with humble beginnings in 2004, by Charanjit Singh, better known as ‘CJ,’ who provided financial and loan services to his clients.  After years of hard work and devotion, the business extended into the building and construction industry, then later into the home/land package options for its customers.

 

The next and most logical progression from there, was for Melvic to apply its already successful business expertise into the real estate market, where Melvic Real Estate Pty Ltd, was later born.

 

Our aim at Melvic Real Estate Pty Ltd, is to not only build a strong relationship with our clients, but to also provide them with the highest level of customer service possible, whether they are looking to sell, buy or are just looking for their next property.

 

Melvic Real Estate Pty Ltd, is conveniently located in Hallam
name: Melvic Real Estate

description: Harvest Realty is part of a dynamic real estate industry in Hampton Park focusing on prospecting, listing, marketing, and presenting properties for sale, thus providing information and negotiating sale terms and conditions to its clientele. It also offers services for property management across a range of property types and performs general office activities including reception, secretarial, bookkeeping and clerical duties to support the real estate personnel to undertake all sales and property management activities on a daily basis. Harvest Realty endeavours to deliver substantial benefits to its employees and its clientele through its services and networking management with excellent quality and highly potential skills. Its aim is to be an outstanding place for the real estate activities by providing very high level of service & quality and well-researched data in the real estate industry for its clientele with the highest degree of integrity and professionalism. Through its personnel’s expertise and experience, Harvest Realty strives to be an excellent role model and a significant player among its competitors for its quality, services and management skills of the business and to compete with the established agencies in Hampton Park, Lynbrook, Narre Warren, Hallam, Berwick, Cranbourne and other surrounding suburbs to accommodate the mentioned needs by providing its clientele with the necessary information of real estate needs and assisting them with important decision in buying, selling or renting a home or investment property.
name: Harvest Realty

Just tell us your needs then we will endevour to find the most suitable property for your choice. Feel free to give us a call to discuss further about your property needs. Happy purchasing:-)

description: Les Donaldson managing director established the office of Donaldson Martin & Co in its prominet location on the corner of Princes Highway and Webb St Narre Warren in 1977. Now spanning two generations our family business is well known and respected within the industry, by our clients and the community. having lived in the area for close on 40 years with a local knowledge second to none the Donaldson family and their business has grown with the once small towns that have now evolved into the City of Casey, now one of the largest growth corridors within Australia with a population in excess of 230,0000. Les, Brett and Dale offer a combined total of in excess of 75 years of Real Estate experience in residential sales and property management, with Les and Brett being acknowledged as some of the most respected, experienced and successful Auctioneers in the district. As members of the Real Estate Institute of Victoria (REIV) we have access to the latest training and data availble, we can provide a personal and professional approach, with the highest levels of service and integrity for all your Real Estate needs. Les, Brett Dale and staff are available to assist you with all aspects of the sale or leasing of your property.
name: Donaldson Martin & Co Pty Ltd

description:
GR8 EST8 AGENTS are an innovative new real estate agency supporting sellers in Melbourne’s southeastern suburbs to save thousands, while selling their homes for more.

 

Our unique business model allows us to cut back on overhead expenses and pass the savings directly on to you. At GR8 EST8 AGENTS, we’re proud to offer a premium sales and marketing package to get you a GR8 Result!

 

Based in the central hub of Narre Warren, our mobile agents operate throughout Casey and surrounding areas providing outstanding results and a highly professional service that you can count on.

 

With one of our 24/7 agents available at all times, we can guarantee you that we’ll be there to support you through any of your out of hours real estate emergencies that may arise.

 

The GR8 EST8 AGENTS team has more than 45 years’ collective experience in the property market, and our agents all have the advantage of living within the local area. With a deep understanding of the local market, you can be assured that our agents possess the knowledge needed to secure a premium price for your property.

 

Trustworthy, transparent and true to our word, the team at GR8 EST8 AGENTS are committed to providing you with continuous communication and delivering a superior level of customer service
name: Gr8 Est8 Agents

description: The Wise Group was formed by two highly regarded real estate professionals with diversified experience in the local market. We are a fully integrated real estate solutions provider ranging from simply buying and selling property to helping you with subdivisions, constructions, project management and property management. We are focused on delivering solutions which will help you meet your future financial goals by building up a valuable property portfolio with good returns. Our customers will immensely benefit from our existing wide network.

In fact, its not only Narre Warren Souths most established real estate agency, its its first. Opened in 2004 by the multi award-winning duo of Rebecca Borg and Brad Ryan, the prominent office is located at the popular Casey Central Shopping Centre, which is also the vibrant, central hub for the City of Caseys ongoing growth and development.
