description:
UpHill is a vibrant and relationship centric real estate venture that has honesty, integrity, dedication, hardwork and transparency in its core

 

With over ten years of combined experience in real estate and over 300 successful sales in the last few years alone, our team has vast experience and knowledge in sales, rentals, appraisals, accounting, marketing, engineering, building and constructing.

 

Our goal is to be your partner in obtaining your dream home, assist you in achieving the highest value for your property or service your investment properties that will assist you with your future goals and dreams.
name: UpHill Real Estate

description:
In 1985, John G. King began building steel frame homes in Ballarat. His vision was to pioneer a new standard of home building, using exclusively Australian made TRUECORE® steel.

In our first year of operations 35 homes were delivered. Today, JG King Homes has grown to a business that proudly builds for over 1,000 families each year. With 10 offices all around Victoria, we’re trusted by families for timeless home designs and safe, strong, highly considered builds.

Despite the recognition and accolades JG King Homes has won over the years, seeing our customers enjoy their homes is still the biggest reward of all.

We are Victoria’s largest builder of steel frame homes, but as a family-owned company, JG King Homes understands the importance of building an unrivalled home.
name: JG King Homes

description:
With a proven track record within senior property management roles in corporate real estate services, corporate relocations, residential, commercial and retail property management, leasing and sales. René now uses her expertise to identify real market opportunities and long term investment propositions for Bayview Property Management clients through her pragmatic approach to property. During her career she has been instrumental in setting up a real estate agency franchise and the re-branding of a well-established real estate agency franchise.

René has worked in the marketing & sales within the property development industry.  René’s career spans more than 17 years within the Australian property industry when she made the move in 2018 to establish Bayview  Property Management.

René is truly passionate about property and understands - The Australian property cycle & the life-cycle of property management; - Research based analysis of the Australian property market;  - Property market dynamics; what, where, when & how to acquire property; - Demographic profiling and how this drives property demand; - Long term assumptions and opportunities of property investment as an asset class.  René is a long term residential property investor. René understands property as both an asset class (facts and figures) and a tangible commodity (touch and feel).  ?René has an intimate understanding of landlords' needs and concerns and a sound knowledge of residential property investment and the legislation governing the management of residential and commercial real estate. René also works as a buyer’s advocate and tenant’s advocate specifically for her corporate relocation clients. René ensures a smooth transition providing trusted guidance and exceptional negotiation skills in securing a tenancy and/or purchase of property.  This experience, along with her clear, calm, direct communication style makes her the ideal person to be managing your property investment on a day to day basis.  

René holds a Victorian Real Estate license. In her down time René & her husband enjoy supporting their 3 daughters in their sport, dance and cheer-leading competitions locally & nationally. Family trips snow-skiing in the Aussie Alps in the winter months & water-skiing the Gippsland Lakes and Bay of Port Phillip in the summer months.  Rene strives to make every property experience enjoyable and rewarding for all concerned. If you want something done (and done right the first time!), René is your perfect choice of property professional.
name: Bayview Property Management

description:
Dandenong Real Estate Agents & Property Management

CENTURY 21 Team , Dandenong

Situated right in the heart of the Dandenong shopping strip on Langhorne Street, Century 21Team Dandenong is ideally positioned for maximum exposure. The location of the office, along with the generous window front means there are excellent display opportunities for both sale and rental properties. 

The Director, Ritesh Saigal and his Team, are committed to working hard to get the best results for all clients be it in Sales or looking after your investment home. A combined experience of Team Century 21 in Dandenong is well over 100 years. We believe that the Dandenong area is ripe with opportunity and is indeed the second city of Melbourne.

The strong and positive recognition the Century 21 banner gives to all properties it sells or manages, is what encourages many people to choose them above all other real estate agents. A global brand like Century 21 and its innovative marketing tools are extremely effective when it comes to selling and managing your property. A network of more than 250 hundred offices in Australia and New Zealand collaborate to help find buyers wherever they are.

Suburbs serviced: Dandenong, Dandenong North, Dandenong South, Keysborough, Doveton, Eumemmerring, Endeavour Hills, Hallam and Hampton Park.
name: Century 21 Team Dandenong

description:
We are a small fresh company with big attributes specialising in Residential, Retail, Commercial Sales and Leasing. We are a strong dynamic team with diverse experiences. We are a team of young professionals with in-depth knowledge, excellent communication, can-do attitude and a commitment to provide exceptional service to our clients. We have a huge amount of experience and knowledge of the area and its surrounds, and due to this we are able to negotiate the best prices for your assets.

Creston is situated in the heart of Dandenong, our range we service is City of Greater Dandenong, City of Kingston and City of Casey but limited to. These areas offer a great mix of old charming homes to newly developed homes which our experienced Sales and Rental team excel in.

Our aim is to build bridges between seller and buyers, landlords and tenants so then only the best results are obtained. We’ll listen to you, guide you in the right direction and do everything possible to provide you a stress-free experience with us.

To enquire om how Creston Dandenong can help you make the right choices for your assets, contact our friendly office on 03 9792 0042
name: Creston Real Estate

description: Del Real Estate is family owned and operated with each family member having a day to day involvement in the sales and property management department, ensuring a close working relationship between the management team and our clients. Our philosophy is to provide professional value-adding service to our clients and with this in mind, we have a strong ongoing commitment to regular training of our staff through the Real Estate Institute of Victoria and specialized real estate workshops and seminars. We are passionate about our role as your real estate advisor and will ensure you are continuously up to date with the progress of selling, leasing and managing of your most valuable asset.
name: Del Real Estate

description:
Good Deal Real Estate strives in bringing and adding value in real estate solutions for both seller and buyer alike. We believe price is what you pay.  Value is what you get.

We endeavour to work smart and hard to achieve a win-win outcome for both the seller and the buyer thus culminating "a good deal" for both parties.

"Making it happen" is our credo.

We believe in taking a proactive, focussed approach towards our clients' needs.

We believe expertise and experience trumps over other qualities particularly when the stakes are so high in any real estate transaction.

So give us that opportunity to bring you a lot more value than the price you will pay.

 Our core suburbs which we operate are Keysborough, Waterways, Springvale, Dingley Village, Noble Park, Dandenong, Hampton Park and Lyndhurst.  However, we do service beyond these suburbs too as along as these are  within reasonable driving time.
name: Good Deal Real Estate

description:
Hall & Partners can trace its origins back to 1917 when Frank Facey commenced trading in Dandenong. In 1956 the company moved to its current office in busy Lonsdale Street.

In 1982 we joined the First National Real Estate group, which gave us the strength and support of 600 offices throughout  Australia and New Zealand.

Michael Hall purchased the Dandenong Office from the Facey family in 1990 and his son Leigh, along with Nicole Knecht are partners in the firm, all of whom are actively involved in the day to day running of the business. 

Whilst being proud of our history it was decided in 2005 to move our emphasis to the future, consequently we changed our name to Hall & Partners First National, which reflects the true ownership of the company.

Our team of experienced professionals are well established in the area and provide the highest level of service to the local community which includes listing properties on multiple web sites, a local property magazine and marketing via our inhouse marketing department.
name: Hall & Partners First National Dandenong

description:
In an increasingly fast-paced world, Harcourts Dandenong knows that while people want a professional and efficient service, they still prize the fundamentals of honesty and integrity from real estate consultants committed to achieving their clients’ goals.

That’s why Harcourts Dandenong combines world-renowned technology, training and systems with a focus on establishing trust and respect with their clients who always remain at the centre of the process.

Whether you’re buying, selling or renting residential property, Harcourts Dandenong is proud to offer a service which continually delivers superior results and exceeds client expectations.

 

Harcourts Dandenong's Values:

  • People First
  • Doing the right thing
  • Being courageous
  • Fun and Laughter
name: Harcourts Asap Group

description:
One of the most professional and innovative real estate agencies in the region, Hockingstuart Dandenong is dedicated to delivering exceptional customer service with professionalism, integrity and outstanding results.

Led by principal Jack Miltos, our highly skilled team has a community approach to their work and offer outstanding local knowledge to help every client achieve their property goals. With attributes such as knowledge, skill and compassion at our core, weve brought enormous success to numerous clients across the region.
name: Hockingstuart Dandenong

description:
Welcome to LJ Hooker Dandenong City.

Our objective is to protect and expand on both the financial and physical wellbeing of your real estate assets and to provide you with the highest level of customer service possible. 

With a team of highly astute negotiators, LJ Hooker Dandenong offers a full range of property services including sales and property management.
name: LJ Hooker Dandenong

description: <center style="text-align: start;"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Ray White brings you unparalleled technology, dedication and a real passion for customer service, so you can be sure whether you list, sell, rent or buy with us - you’re getting real estate experts with a local feel.</font></center>
name: Ray White Dandenong

description:
An office with a long history in one area is an office with extensive local knowledge, market know-how and a long history of success.  

Stockdale & Leggo Dandenong – widely regarded as the local agency of choice for sales results, auction success, and professional property management – was established in the early 1970s.

It has also since evolved with the changing area, buyer demographics, and the ever-changing property industry to remain at the forefront of innovative, cutting-edge real estate service provision and results.  

The award-winning office is well known as the local auction specialist – for both auction numbers and success rates – throughout Dandenong, Endeavour Hills, Hallam, Doveton, Noble Park, Keysborough and surrounds. The team has conducted some 100 auctions per year for the last 20 years, well outstripping numbers conducted by others in the area. More importantly, their clearance rate exceeds 90%, which is significantly higher than the industry average.

The office – comprising a large, expert team of multi-lingual professionals – enjoys a strong reputation, loyal base of repeat and referral clients, and positive working relationships with its valued clients. “We work within a culture of success that goes back some 40 years,” says Neil. “Putting in 100% - whether we’re invited into someone’s home to conduct an appraisal or screening for the best tenants for our landlords – is the only way we know.”  

 The office is a multiple recipient of the prestigious Stockdale & Leggo Gold Achievement Award for its consistently high levels of professional excellence and results. It is also consistently positioned as one of the top performing offices in the entire Stockdale & Leggo network.
name: Stockdale & Leggo Dandenong

description:
As the name implies, at Berwick Estate Agents, we're locals. We love our community and have a deep understanding of our local property market. With a combined real estate experience of 60 years, the team at Berwick Estate Agents, owned and operated by John Sprakel, takes the time to understand what it is you need and then partners with you to provide a tailored service that caters to your unique circumstances. Whether you're looking to buy or sell, rent or lease, upgrade or downsize, invest or occupy the team at Berwick Estate Agents have the expertise to ensure the entire experience is hassle free and gets you the best result at the best price.


Our team specialises in properties found in Berwick, Beaconsfield, Narre Warren, Narre Warren South, Narre Warren North, Clyde North, Clyde, Cranbourne North, Cranbourne, Hallam, Endeavour Hills Officer and Pakenham. Experts in all areas of real estate Whether you're a first time buyer or an experienced investor, looking for the perfect rental property or the right tenants, downsizing or looking for the right home to raise a family, at Berwick Estate Agebnts we can help you take that next step. Take a few moments to meet our team of experienced real estate professionals, then give us a call on 03 9796 2666 to discuss how we can help you realise your property dreams.
name: Berwick Estate Agents

description:
Elite Agents & Partners was established to bring together the most experienced and highly regarded group of people in the real estate space and have created a model that is more responsive to today's property market.

We are an innovative agency using proven sales & marketing strategies which deliver the best outcomes for our local and international clientele. Our team delivers excellence on all fronts from client satisfaction and smart marketing to expert negotiation and exceptional results. If you are considering selling, please call us on 0413 495 802.
name: Elite Agents & Partners

description: Morrison Commercial operates as specialist Industrial and Commercial Property Consultants.  The Company has built its reputation on loyalty to its clients, honesty and sound marketing advice, supported by strong Property Management, Owners Corporation and Property Development and Investment Divisions.
name: Morrison Commercial Industrial

description:
Pyramid property management is dedicated property management firm based in the city of Monash. The company offers benchmark customer service, negotiation and marketing strategies to the clients. With the company’s goal being, first and foremost, to provide a profitable and positive real estate experience for all clients, Pyramid property management works each day to ensure the client comes first while a timely service is provided that meets or exceeds all expectations.

It is not uncommon in property management that clients do not get the level of service that they expected. Both directors of Pyramid Property Management believe that there are ways of managing properties more effectively and most importantly delivering on promises to the clients.

As an active member of Real Estate Institute of Victoria, Pyramid property Management is continually updating new systems and following recent changes in property management to ensure that the clients get up to date information.

With a very high regard for customer service, something that is paramount in the real estate industry, Pyramid Property management is proud that the majority of their business comes from repeat clients or family and friends. We hope that each customer could share their success stories with friends, family and acquaintances and be our “Customer for Life.”
name: Pyramid Property Management

description: Boutique Estate Agency represents a genuine hands on approach which will lead the way in local real estate services. Located on the border of Dandenong North and Mulgrave whilst covering a wide network of suburbs from Clayton right through to Berwick makes Boutique Estate Agency able to cater to a large portion of the south eastern suburbs.
name: Boutique Estate Agency

description:
Platinum Real Estate is a tech savvy residential real estate agency that emphasizes innovation, integrity, and results in the representation of its clients. Whether you are searching for a new home or contemplating selling, our team is quick to respond and committed to superior customer service.

The result at Platinum is a unique real estate experience achieved through top class representation, complete information and superior communication. We are fortunate to have resources that rival the largest agencies and because we are locally owned we are able to provide you with extraordinary care.
name: Platinum Real Estate

description:
Who is Nicholls Gledhill?

Nicholls Gledhill is the longest operating agency in Endeavour Hills. It is not part of another franchise chain but an independent owner-operated family business managed by Harry Nicholls who started the company himself 40 years ago.

Harry is also a Certified Practising Valuer (AAPI), the only one in Endeavour Hills, an associate of the Real estate Institute of Victoria (AREI) and a past president of the REIV (Waverley Branch).

Other staff includes Harry’s son Matthew Nicholls (Office Manager) Laurel Heath (Rental Property Manager) who has had years of experience in this specialised field of real estate plus our dedicated team of sales, reception and clerical staff.

The fact that we operate from our own premises within the Terrace Shopping Centre means that we do not have the substantial overheads experienced by our competitors, expenses such as franchise fees, high shopping centre rentals, group advertising levies etc. Consequently we can offer a more experienced and professional service at more competitive rates.

In order to further improve our service to clients we have just taken over the adjacent premises and have totally refurbished our newly enlarged office complex.

As a result we can now boast the most impressive modern real estate office in the district as well as the biggest and best window display which is kept right up to date with all the best and latest listings. This display works day and night, week-in, week-out attracting potential buyers seeking home in the area. Undoubtedly the best possible place to present your home to the market.
name: Nicholls Gledhill

description:
The #1 Endeavour Hills Real Estate Agents

The last twelve months have been an exciting time for us. We have successfully taken the number one spot for real estate agents in Endeavour Hills by a wide margin, working hard for our vendors to achieve the very best possible prices. With convenient access to the city and major shopping centres, as well as beautiful walking tracks and parkland, this area is a fantastic location for people looking to buy. This is one of the reasons why we have been so successful in helping many satisfied vendors in finding the best price.

Why we’re number one
Here at O’Brien Real Estate Endeavour Hills, we ensure to take care of each and every one of our vendors. Our team of qualified and enthusiastic agents will go above and beyond to achieve the best possible sales result every time, no exceptions. Our sole concern is the outcome we accomplish for our clients, because at the end of the day a business such as this is primarily based on our past successes and the testimonials of our previous clients.

As this is always at the front of our minds, we are able to approach each sales process individually, with the enthusiasm and commitment that you should expect when selling your property. This is just one of the reasons why we have managed to take majority of the market share in just under 12 months, currently residing at a commanding 31%. Another contributing factor is our dedicated team, which is fortunate enough to have the leading agents in the Endeavour Hills area, vendors can rest assured that we’ll get them the best prices, every time.

Property Rental Management Services
Further to our leading sales agents, we provide an extensive and professional team of rental property managers, to remove any and all stresses that have a habit of showing up when you decide to buy an investment property and get into the rental market. Our managers have a great deal of experience to safeguard your investment, and ensure you get the rental payments on time.

Talk to us today

To book in an appraisal for your property by one of our estate agents, or if you’d like to have a discussion with a representative from our property management team, please get in touch with us today on (03) 8768 0400. We have specialised teams dealing with suburbs throughout the South East of Melbourne including Berwick, Cranbourne, and Narre Warren just to name a few.
name: OBrien Real Estate Endeavour Hills

description:
Mindacom is a specialist 'niche marketing' Consultant with extensive experience in all aspects of Commercial, Industrial and Residential Real Estate.

We have an extensive - and impressive - client base and the vast majority of its business turnover is derived from past clientele or personal recommendation.

The business commenced in 1989 and has continued to expand and diversify under the guidance of Managing Director, Mary O'Halloran.

Contact us for all your Commercial, Industrial and Residential Real Estate needs in Braeside, Mordialloc, Mentone, Cheltenham, Edithvale, Dingley, Moorabbin, Dandenong, Frankston and surrounding areas of Melbourne.
name: Mindacom Real Estate

description:
Our company-Melvic, (derived from Melbourne and Victoria,) began with humble beginnings in 2004, by Charanjit Singh, better known as ‘CJ,’ who provided financial and loan services to his clients.  After years of hard work and devotion, the business extended into the building and construction industry, then later into the home/land package options for its customers.

 

The next and most logical progression from there, was for Melvic to apply its already successful business expertise into the real estate market, where Melvic Real Estate Pty Ltd, was later born.

 

Our aim at Melvic Real Estate Pty Ltd, is to not only build a strong relationship with our clients, but to also provide them with the highest level of customer service possible, whether they are looking to sell, buy or are just looking for their next property.

 

Melvic Real Estate Pty Ltd, is conveniently located in Hallam
name: Melvic Real Estate

description: Harvest Realty is part of a dynamic real estate industry in Hampton Park focusing on prospecting, listing, marketing, and presenting properties for sale, thus providing information and negotiating sale terms and conditions to its clientele. It also offers services for property management across a range of property types and performs general office activities including reception, secretarial, bookkeeping and clerical duties to support the real estate personnel to undertake all sales and property management activities on a daily basis. Harvest Realty endeavours to deliver substantial benefits to its employees and its clientele through its services and networking management with excellent quality and highly potential skills. Its aim is to be an outstanding place for the real estate activities by providing very high level of service & quality and well-researched data in the real estate industry for its clientele with the highest degree of integrity and professionalism. Through its personnel’s expertise and experience, Harvest Realty strives to be an excellent role model and a significant player among its competitors for its quality, services and management skills of the business and to compete with the established agencies in Hampton Park, Lynbrook, Narre Warren, Hallam, Berwick, Cranbourne and other surrounding suburbs to accommodate the mentioned needs by providing its clientele with the necessary information of real estate needs and assisting them with important decision in buying, selling or renting a home or investment property.
name: Harvest Realty

description:
Our commitment is to ADVISE, HELP & CARE FOR YOU. 

We will provide you with the utmost care, consideration, ethics & honesty as your real estate agent of choice.

The successful sale and purchase of your home, investment or development is usually the single most important transaction you will make in your life, and is therefore high up on the list of potentially stressful situations.

Good communication on our part will help reduce these stresses and make your sale go through smoothly and efficiently and hopefully bring you, your family and friends back to us for your future property needs.

We will be here to help guide you through every step of your real estate journey.

Whether it is to find you your first home, investment or development site, we will be here to liaise with the wide range of people including solicitors, plumbers, cleaners, gardeners and builders to ensure that everything runs smoothly so you need have no concerns.

At Raine & Horne Keysborough we will give you three times the level of service, we will provide you with an experienced & qualified team with three times the levels of enthusiasm, commitment and support which you may not have experienced before, in order for you to achieve the finest real estate experience which will keep you coming back to us again and again and again.
name: Sovereign Properties
Frasers Property | VIC

description:
Established and owned by fifth generation Melbourne property identities, Michael and Andrew Buxton, MAB has activities in residential, retail, industrial and commercial developments, as well as a funds management business.
 
With an unrivalled ability to deliver on complex planning outcomes for major projects and an established track record of creating outstanding public places; our people are committed to the vision of producing quality developments.
 
By daring to imagine such visionary projects as NewQuay, Docklands and University Hill in Bundoora, MAB is playing a significant role in reshaping the environments in which we live, work and play.
 
In a joint venture with Gibson Property Corporation (GPC), MAB has now embarked on its largest and most visionary development to date, Merrifield, a new city for Melbourne comprising more than 900 hectares located on the Hume Highway in Mickleham.
 
We are building an enviable reputation for quality and establishing our business as one which thrives on challenge and opportunity.
name: MAB Corporation

description:
Family owned and operated business located at Waverley Gardens Shopping Centre, Mulgrave for over 30 years under the First National Umbrella. Our Principal Adrian Hall took over back in 2003. With a background in marketing prior to taking over, it is evident that this has flowed through to the way First National AC & Co promotes properties for sale. This coupled with the huge exposure we get ensures that customers are left satisfied and gives us a huge competitive advantage.

 For all your real estate needs whether you are thinking of selling, buying or leasing out your property please do not hesitate to call our principal, Adrian Hall directly on 0417 123 820.
name: First National Real Estate AC & CO

description: Les Donaldson managing director established the office of Donaldson Martin & Co in its prominet location on the corner of Princes Highway and Webb St Narre Warren in 1977. Now spanning two generations our family business is well known and respected within the industry, by our clients and the community. having lived in the area for close on 40 years with a local knowledge second to none the Donaldson family and their business has grown with the once small towns that have now evolved into the City of Casey, now one of the largest growth corridors within Australia with a population in excess of 230,0000. Les, Brett and Dale offer a combined total of in excess of 75 years of Real Estate experience in residential sales and property management, with Les and Brett being acknowledged as some of the most respected, experienced and successful Auctioneers in the district. As members of the Real Estate Institute of Victoria (REIV) we have access to the latest training and data availble, we can provide a personal and professional approach, with the highest levels of service and integrity for all your Real Estate needs. Les, Brett Dale and staff are available to assist you with all aspects of the sale or leasing of your property.
name: Donaldson Martin & Co Pty Ltd

address1: Office S1003, Fountain Gate Shopping Centre,
description:
Narre Warren’s Supreme Real Estate Agents

 

With so many schools in the area, this suburb is brilliant for family life. Also boasting the impressively large Westfield Fountain Gate shopping centre as well as shopping and cafes around the train station, its amenities are a great feature.

The search for a real estate agent or property manager that has in-depth knowledge of the area as well as an understanding of the housing climate can prove to be a difficult one. At O’Brien Real Estate Narre Warren branch, you can rest assured that we possess the knowledge of the area that will ensure the best result for you, whether you’re selling or have a rental investment.

How we differentiate ourselves from other agencies
Our primary focus from beginning to end of the sales process is you. Unlike some other establishments, we see communication with our vendors and clients as a highly important piece of the puzzle, ensuring you’re always up to date with the latest news. Any questions you have throughout the journey, we are there to discuss with you and help you understand everything that’s happening. The many decades of collective experience we have at O’Brien Real Estate Narre Warren has allowed us to fine-tune our practices, whether that be our sales agents or property management team.

We know exactly how stressful it can be selling a home, and as a result every one of our agents handles the process with professional tact with a sense of compassion. It’s most likely the largest investment we will make, and we act accordingly.

Why you should choose us
Real estate businesses are measured by past successes and referral business is the most important lead generation path we have. That’s exactly why we work tirelessly to get the very best result for every single vendor and client. As testament to this, our team obtained 32 exclusive listings in July 2015 alone. All of our real estate agents are trained from the ground up, with a focus on identifying potential opportunities for our vendors and the ability to always adapt with the ever shifting property landscape.

This high quality training has made us the first choice for vendors looking to portray their property in the most favourable light and to achieve a premium sales price. Not only that, but we aim to go above and beyond for our vendors, organising weekly meetings with them to touch base and ensure their properties are being given the attention they deserve.

Professional rental property managers
Not only can we offer sales agents, but also have a great property management team to ensure your rental is well taken care of and without problems. Be sure to contact us today to find out more.

Call for a free appraisal now!
Our expert agents can give you a free appraisal, and our property management staff can take care of your rental. Call 03 8794 0500 to discuss either. We work right around the South East of Melbourne, including in Cranbourne, Pakenham, and Berwick just to name a few.
name: OBrien Real Estate Narre Warren

description:
We are committed to providing exceptional levels of service & advice for our clients. We stay at the forefront of Real Estate practice & innovation, taking the time to understand & appreciate clients’ needs, understanding intimately the local market & trends, & continually striving to improve the quality & value of our services. We believe that we offer to you the cutting edge on our competitors:

• We have a seller log in system.  When you sell your property with us, you can log in to your personal Century 21 user page & see all the activity that has taken place that day & so far into your campaign.  The site functions 24 hours a day 7 days a week.
• We have achieved the highest sales price for a house in the area, a unit and also land.
• If you chose to Auction your property, you will have the benefit of Travis Bockman, an award winning Auctioneer conducting your auction.
• All members of the Team from the front desk to the Director are consistently trained both at a corporate level & also in house
• We offer a New Projects focused division for builders & also buyers, this makes the process smooth identifying stages of building & projects
• Between the 18 staff members working with our office we can speak Vietnamese, Chinese, Cambodian, Mandarin, Arabic, Cantonese & English
• Being an International brand, this helps with recognition of our brand & also directs buyers, sellers & tenants to our web site both nationally & internationally increasing the exposure of all of our advertised properties

• Inter office selling has seen our Clayton, Clarinda & Springvale offices assist in the sales of numerous houses within our core business area assisting us to achieve excellent prices for our customers

Noble Park, Keysborough and the City of Greater Dandenong are truly some of the most sought after areas in Victoria and this has assisted us in reaching the number 1 status in the Century 21 Victorian network on many levels, we’d love to assist you with your real estate needs as well.
name: Century 21 Wilson Pride

description: Established in 1988, Ray White Noble Park has become one of the leading offices in the Ray White Network and consistently ranks as a Top 4 Victorian Office. The Team at Noble Park enjoys a high profile both within the group and locally. Our reputation in sales results and dedication to superior service has established us as the leading and most successful agent in the area. Principals Graeme Oldmeadow and Allison Grant, together with their highly trained and professional team, occupy a prominent main street office. The stunning window display offers a showcase of homes with huge exposure to busy Douglas Street. We have a significant investment in computer technology to assist us in the delivery of accurate sales information, together with prompt and effective service. The office proudly supports many community groups and sporting clubs and donates time to conduct annual charity auctions. Ray White Noble Park also has a professionally run property management and investment department. Our investors benefit from the knowledge, experience and service that we provide, which ensures the protection of your investment. We are proud of our reputation and undertake to keep you informed with the state of the market and how it affects your situation. Whether you are selling, buying, leasing or just simply seeking 'the right advice', you will benefit from our vast experience and the overall strength of the Ray White Group with over 560 offices.
name: Ray White Noble Park

description:
At Ray White Rowville we work harder for our customers.

Backed with over 116 years of experience from Australasia’s largest real estate group, Ray White Rowville clients can rest assured that they have selected the right team.

Having established themselves as market leaders in the Knox area, we know firsthand what makes the area and the lifestyle attractive. What’s more, we know what motivates buyers in the local market.

Our comprehensive past client and buyer database ensures that your property is presented to more genuine buyers, to maximise the competition to buy your property. During the campaign, we use a refined set of processes that have been specifically designed to get you the best possible price for your property.

When you choose an agent at Ray White Rowville, you get the support of our full team. Our unique structure encourages all agents to work together to achieve the best price for your property. With over 1,000 offices across 11 countries, we can also connect you to buyers from all over the world. This international exposure is an added dimension no other agency can rival.

We pride ourselves on providing an exceptional level of personal and professional service to make the selling process easy and rewarding for all our clients.
name: Ray White Rowville

description:
When it comes to selling or leasing commercial property it is best to entrust it to hockingstuart Commercial – the people who have the necessary know-how and experience to expertly handle these highly specialised transactions for you.

 hockingstuart’s Commercial division deals in commercial properties in all suburbs and constantly monitors sales results and rental levels across the board so their clients can have ready access to the most up-to-the-minute information at all times.

 Our team is thoroughly conversant with the complexities of leases, the implications of the GST and the associated legal requirements associated with commercial real estate.
name: Belle Property Commercial South Melbourne

description:
We at iSell group have identified a need for a more fresh and progressive approach to real estate in Melbourne’s South East.

We intend to fill this need. We are boutique in style, informal yet professional, proud but not arrogant, skilled yet continuously trained. We are experienced but not stale, eager to impress, always thrilled at being able to help our client’s. We never lose the “first day at work” excitement.

We approach our work with the highest degree of motivation, it’s more than a career… it’s like our oxygen! We strive to become the market leaders in the City of Greater Dandenong and surrounds. We hope with you as our client, we can achieve this in time. We believe in making decisions in ways to best serve our clients interest. Not surprisingly this philosophy has enabled us to help more clients and we love it!
name: iSell Group

description:
At Le & Co, we draw on over 25 years’ combined industry experience to deliver a rare combination of expertise, excellence and care. With an unparalleled understanding of the south-eastern suburbs of Melbourne, we specialize in providing real estate agency service to the dynamic hub of Springvale.
Founded by the industry-respected Le brothers, Le & Co is a team of passionate, proactive and high-performing professionals.
When you partner with Le & Co, you can be confident that our knowledge becomes your asset. We promise to leave no stone unturned in our quest to achieve the greatest outcome for you.
name: Le & Co Estate Agents

description:
Leyton Real Estate is a leading, boutique real estate agency offering sales, leasing and property management services.  When we opened the doors of Leyton Real Estate in 2007, our mission was clear.. to offer professional, courteous and straightforward service for people selling, buying or leasing in Melbourne's South East. Almost a decade later we continue working to surpass these goals for all our clients.

ATTRACTING THE RIGHT BUYERS identifying and engaging relevant buyers for your property is one of our core strengths. We have one of the largest databases in South Eastern suburbs of Melbourne; our database includes both local and overseas investors.  This enables us to identify buyers whose criteria match your property. This approach is further complemented by our ability to locate buyers through our local community referral network.

LEYTON TEAM  Our multi-lingual team is staffed by professionals in a range of fields... from sales, to marketing, auctioneering, property management and administration both Residential and Commercial. This gives us the ability to provide enhanced cultural understanding to our clients. The result is less ambiguity in the sales and leasing process and more satisfied clients who feel more informed and in control.

LOCAL EXPERTISE Our intimate knowledge of the local property market is unsurpassed, enabling us to provide the highest quality advise and insight, our strong focus and customised approach to client service that sets us apart. Our team is well informed, professional and dedicated.  We are passionate about Real Estate and whole-heartedly love what we do!

TRANSPARENCY  We place a premium on transparency and clarity. We share information and develop business relationships built on trust.  Our ethical approach and our professional standards has been the foundation of Leyton's business growth. It has allowed us to be recognised as one of the most reputable and trusted agencies in the local community. We are confident that we can meet your property needs and we welcome the opportunity to work with you in the future.

COMMUNITY FOCUS

Finally, we believe in supporting our local community and continue to invest in Springvale Snow Fest, Local sporting bodies and the Royal Children's Hospital. We love Real Estate and we're passionate about our community. It’s just one way we can help to make a difference.
name: Leyton Real Estate

description:
PAUL JONES REALTY was established in 1984 under the leadership of Paul Vazirianis, who had a vision in creating an Estate Agency that, would provide the upmost professionalism in real estate sales and property management, specialising and servicing the South Eastern suburbs of Melbourne and beyond.

Our office is strategically located on the busy corner of Springvale Road and Union Grove Springvale and provides our clients the highest exposure to show case their properties.

As an independent and boutique real estate agency, we are able to provide a service that is far superior to our competitors, with our management team personally handling the sale and management of your property.

Our mission is to set the highest standard of excellence and to exceed our client’s expectations with excellent service and integrity. Throughout the entire process, we are committed to making the sale and the management of your property an easy and rewarding experience.

Our dedicated and knowledgeable sales, management and administration team and our distinctive brand, enables us to offer a first class range of services to our clients, who prefer to deal with an agency offering personalised real estate service, rather than dealing with a large chain real estate office.

Our specialist approach in marketing properties has resulted in thousands of satisfied customers. We allow time and energy to be spent on a personalised campaign that is individually designed for each property. This ensures maximum, dedicated service to our vendors, which helps ensure that the right buyer is found for each individual property.

Our people are highly reputable, well trained and dedicated to achieving outstanding results. Our Property Management, Sales and Administrative staff is equally committed to achieving outstanding results for our clients

We are totally committed to making every step of the process a positive and pleasant experience whilst working to ensure that the best possible result is achieved for you - the Vendor. 

As a member of the Real Estate Institute of Victoria, we're committed to a strict code of Conduct and Rules of Professional Practice. Our REIV membership means an ethical and professional approach to business and a sense of community spirit.

Appointing Paul Jones Realty and experience a highly professional organisation in action, focused on achieving the best possible result for our clients.
name: Paul Jones Realty

description:
Eastpoint Property Consultants are a recognised force in Sales, Leasing & Management Services in Commercial and Industrial real estate throughout Melbourne and its surrounding suburbs.

 

A young and innovative company with a mature approach, Eastpoint Property Consultants make owning property easy by providing comprehensive management services. Our team of property managers not only specialise in rental and outgoings recovery. They are also experienced in Owners Corporation liaison, Essential Services Co-ordination, OH&S Legislation compliance and all major areas of concern to our investors.

 

Lead by Director Ralph Herrmann, the company is driven to provide professional investment sales and leasing advice that is second to none and ensures that your property decision will suit your individual needs.

 

If you are looking for independent advice on your next portfolio purchase or tenancy leasing, please call Eastpoint Property Consultants on (03) 8561 5200.

description: Boutique Estate Agency represents a genuine hands on approach which will lead the way in local real estate services. description:
Dandenong Real Estate Agents & Property Management

CENTURY 21 Team , Dandenong

Situated right in the heart of the Dandenong shopping strip on Langhorne Street, Century 21Team Dandenong is ideally positioned for maximum exposure. The location of the office, along with the generous window front means there are excellent display opportunities for both sale and rental properties. 

The Director, Ritesh Saigal and his Team, are committed to working hard to get the best results for all clients be it in Sales or looking after your investment home. A combined experience of Team Century 21 in Dandenong is well over 100 years. We believe that the Dandenong area is ripe with opportunity and is indeed the second city of Melbourne.

The strong and positive recognition the Century 21 banner gives to all properties it sells or manages, is what encourages many people to choose them above all other real estate agents. A global brand like Century 21 and its innovative marketing tools are extremely effective when it comes to selling and managing your property. A network of more than 250 hundred offices in Australia and New Zealand collaborate to help find buyers wherever they are.

Suburbs serviced: Dandenong, Dandenong North, Dandenong South, Keysborough, Doveton, Eumemmerring, Endeavour Hills, Hallam and Hampton Park.
name: Century 21 Team Dandenong

description:
We are a small fresh company with big attributes specialising in Residential, Retail, Commercial Sales and Leasing. We are a strong dynamic team with diverse experiences. We are a team of young professionals with in-depth knowledge, excellent communication, can-do attitude and a commitment to provide exceptional service to our clients. We have a huge amount of experience and knowledge of the area and its surrounds, and due to this we are able to negotiate the best prices for your assets.

Creston is situated in the heart of Dandenong, our range we service is City of Greater Dandenong, City of Kingston and City of Casey but limited to. These areas offer a great mix of old charming homes to newly developed homes which our experienced Sales and Rental team excel in.

Our aim is to build bridges between seller and buyers, landlords and tenants so then only the best results are obtained. We’ll listen to you, guide you in the right direction and do everything possible to provide you a stress-free experience with us.

To enquire om how Creston Dandenong can help you make the right choices for your assets, contact our friendly office on 03 9792 0042
name: Creston Real Estate

description: Del Real Estate is family owned and operated with each family member having a day to day involvement in the sales and property management department, ensuring a close working relationship between the management team and our clients. Our philosophy is to provide professional value-adding service to our clients and with this in mind, we have a strong ongoing commitment to regular training of our staff through the Real Estate Institute of Victoria and specialized real estate workshops and seminars. We are passionate about our role as your real estate advisor and will ensure you are continuously up to date with the progress of selling, leasing and managing of your most valuable asset.
name: Del Real Estate

description:
Hall & Partners can trace its origins back to 1917 when Frank Facey commenced trading in Dandenong. In 1956 the company moved to its current office in busy Lonsdale Street.

In 1982 we joined the First National Real Estate group, which gave us the strength and support of 600 offices throughout  Australia and New Zealand.

Michael Hall purchased the Dandenong Office from the Facey family in 1990 and his son Leigh, along with Nicole Knecht are partners in the firm, all of whom are actively involved in the day to day running of the business. 

Whilst being proud of our history it was decided in 2005 to move our emphasis to the future, consequently we changed our name to Hall & Partners First National, which reflects the true ownership of the company.

Our team of experienced professionals are well established in the area and provide the highest level of service to the local community which includes listing properties on multiple web sites, a local property magazine and marketing via our inhouse marketing department.
name: Hall & Partners First National Dandenong

Harcourts Dandenong's Values:

description:
The #1 Endeavour Hills Real Estate Agents

The last twelve months have been an exciting time for us. We have successfully taken the number one spot for real estate agents in Endeavour Hills by a wide margin, working hard for our vendors to achieve the very best possible prices. With convenient access to the city and major shopping centres, as well as beautiful walking tracks and parkland, this area is a fantastic location for people looking to buy. This is one of the reasons why we have been so successful in helping many satisfied vendors in finding the best price.

Why we’re number one
Here at O’Brien Real Estate Endeavour Hills, we ensure to take care of each and every one of our vendors. Our team of qualified and enthusiastic agents will go above and beyond to achieve the best possible sales result every time, no exceptions. Our sole concern is the outcome we accomplish for our clients, because at the end of the day a business such as this is primarily based on our past successes and the testimonials of our previous clients.

As this is always at the front of our minds, we are able to approach each sales process individually, with the enthusiasm and commitment that you should expect when selling your property. This is just one of the reasons why we have managed to take majority of the market share in just under 12 months, currently residing at a commanding 31%. Another contributing factor is our dedicated team, which is fortunate enough to have the leading agents in the Endeavour Hills area, vendors can rest assured that we’ll get them the best prices, every time.

Property Rental Management Services
Further to our leading sales agents, we provide an extensive and professional team of rental property managers, to remove any and all stresses that have a habit of showing up when you decide to buy an investment property and get into the rental market. Our managers have a great deal of experience to safeguard your investment, and ensure you get the rental payments on time.

Talk to us today

To book in an appraisal for your property by one of our estate agents, or if you’d like to have a discussion with a representative from our property management team, please get in touch with us today on (03) 8768 0400. We have specialised teams dealing with suburbs throughout the South East of Melbourne including Berwick, Cranbourne, and Narre Warren just to name a few.
name: OBrien Real Estate Endeavour Hills

description:
Family owned and operated business located at Waverley Gardens Shopping Centre, Mulgrave for over 30 years under the First National Umbrella. Our Principal Adrian Hall took over back in 2003. With a background in marketing prior to taking over, it is evident that this has flowed through to the way First National AC & Co promotes properties for sale. This coupled with the huge exposure we get ensures that customers are left satisfied and gives us a huge competitive advantage.

 For all your real estate needs whether you are thinking of selling, buying or leasing out your property please do not hesitate to call our principal, Adrian Hall directly on 0417 123 820.
name: First National Real Estate AC & CO

address1: Office S1003, Fountain Gate Shopping Centre,
description:
Narre Warren’s Supreme Real Estate Agents

 

With so many schools in the area, this suburb is brilliant for family life. Also boasting the impressively large Westfield Fountain Gate shopping centre as well as shopping and cafes around the train station, its amenities are a great feature.

The search for a real estate agent or property manager that has in-depth knowledge of the area as well as an understanding of the housing climate can prove to be a difficult one. At O’Brien Real Estate Narre Warren branch, you can rest assured that we possess the knowledge of the area that will ensure the best result for you, whether you’re selling or have a rental investment.

How we differentiate ourselves from other agencies
Our primary focus from beginning to end of the sales process is you. Unlike some other establishments, we see communication with our vendors and clients as a highly important piece of the puzzle, ensuring you’re always up to date with the latest news. Any questions you have throughout the journey, we are there to discuss with you and help you understand everything that’s happening. The many decades of collective experience we have at O’Brien Real Estate Narre Warren has allowed us to fine-tune our practices, whether that be our sales agents or property management team.

We know exactly how stressful it can be selling a home, and as a result every one of our agents handles the process with professional tact with a sense of compassion. It’s most likely the largest investment we will make, and we act accordingly.

Why you should choose us
Real estate businesses are measured by past successes and referral business is the most important lead generation path we have. That’s exactly why we work tirelessly to get the very best result for every single vendor and client. As testament to this, our team obtained 32 exclusive listings in July 2015 alone. All of our real estate agents are trained from the ground up, with a focus on identifying potential opportunities for our vendors and the ability to always adapt with the ever shifting property landscape.

This high quality training has made us the first choice for vendors looking to portray their property in the most favourable light and to achieve a premium sales price. Not only that, but we aim to go above and beyond for our vendors, organising weekly meetings with them to touch base and ensure their properties are being given the attention they deserve.

Professional rental property managers
Not only can we offer sales agents, but also have a great property management team to ensure your rental is well taken care of and without problems. Be sure to contact us today to find out more.

Call for a free appraisal now!
Our expert agents can give you a free appraisal, and our property management staff can take care of your rental. Call 03 8794 0500 to discuss either. We work right around the South East of Melbourne, including in Cranbourne, Pakenham, and Berwick just to name a few.
name: OBrien Real Estate Narre Warren

description:
We are committed to providing exceptional levels of service & advice for our clients. We stay at the forefront of Real Estate practice & innovation, taking the time to understand & appreciate clients’ needs, understanding intimately the local market & trends, & continually striving to improve the quality & value of our services. We believe that we offer to you the cutting edge on our competitors:

• We have a seller log in system.  When you sell your property with us, you can log in to your personal Century 21 user page & see all the activity that has taken place that day & so far into your campaign.  The site functions 24 hours a day 7 days a week.
• We have achieved the highest sales price for a house in the area, a unit and also land.
• If you chose to Auction your property, you will have the benefit of Travis Bockman, an award winning Auctioneer conducting your auction.
• All members of the Team from the front desk to the Director are consistently trained both at a corporate level & also in house
• We offer a New Projects focused division for builders & also buyers, this makes the process smooth identifying stages of building & projects
• Between the 18 staff members working with our office we can speak Vietnamese, Chinese, Cambodian, Mandarin, Arabic, Cantonese & English
• Being an International brand, this helps with recognition of our brand & also directs buyers, sellers & tenants to our web site both nationally & internationally increasing the exposure of all of our advertised properties

• Inter office selling has seen our Clayton, Clarinda & Springvale offices assist in the sales of numerous houses within our core business area assisting us to achieve excellent prices for our customers

Noble Park, Keysborough and the City of Greater Dandenong are truly some of the most sought after areas in Victoria and this has assisted us in reaching the number 1 status in the Century 21 Victorian network on many levels, we’d love to assist you with your real estate needs as well.
name: Century 21 Wilson Pride

description: Established in 1988, Ray White Noble Park has become one of the leading offices in the Ray White Network and consistently ranks as a Top 4 Victorian Office. The Team at Noble Park enjoys a high profile both within the group and locally. Our reputation in sales results and dedication to superior service has established us as the leading and most successful agent in the area. Principals Graeme Oldmeadow and Allison Grant, together with their highly trained and professional team, occupy a prominent main street office. The stunning window display offers a showcase of homes with huge exposure to busy Douglas Street. We have a significant investment in computer technology to assist us in the delivery of accurate sales information, together with prompt and effective service. The office proudly supports many community groups and sporting clubs and donates time to conduct annual charity auctions. Ray White Noble Park also has a professionally run property management and investment department. Our investors benefit from the knowledge, experience and service that we provide, which ensures the protection of your investment. We are proud of our reputation and undertake to keep you informed with the state of the market and how it affects your situation. Whether you are selling, buying, leasing or just simply seeking 'the right advice', you will benefit from our vast experience and the overall strength of the Ray White Group with over 560 offices.
name: Ray White Noble Park

description:
We at iSell group have identified a need for a more fresh and progressive approach to real estate in Melbourne’s South East.

We intend to fill this need. We are boutique in style, informal yet professional, proud but not arrogant, skilled yet continuously trained. We are experienced but not stale, eager to impress, always thrilled at being able to help our client’s. We never lose the “first day at work” excitement.

We approach our work with the highest degree of motivation, it’s more than a career… it’s like our oxygen! We strive to become the market leaders in the City of Greater Dandenong and surrounds. We hope with you as our client, we can achieve this in time. We believe in making decisions in ways to best serve our clients interest. Not surprisingly this philosophy has enabled us to help more clients and we love it!
name: iSell Group

description:
At Le & Co, we draw on over 25 years’ combined industry experience to deliver a rare combination of expertise, excellence and care. With an unparalleled understanding of the south-eastern suburbs of Melbourne, we specialize in providing real estate agency service to the dynamic hub of Springvale.
Founded by the industry-respected Le brothers, Le & Co is a team of passionate, proactive and high-performing professionals.
When you partner with Le & Co, you can be confident that our knowledge becomes your asset. We promise to leave no stone unturned in our quest to achieve the greatest outcome for you.
name: Le & Co Estate Agents

description:
Leyton Real Estate is a leading, boutique real estate agency offering sales, leasing and property management services.  When we opened the doors of Leyton Real Estate in 2007, our mission was clear.. to offer professional, courteous and straightforward service for people selling, buying or leasing in Melbourne's South East. Almost a decade later we continue working to surpass these goals for all our clients.

ATTRACTING THE RIGHT BUYERS identifying and engaging relevant buyers for your property is one of our core strengths. We have one of the largest databases in South Eastern suburbs of Melbourne; our database includes both local and overseas investors.  This enables us to identify buyers whose criteria match your property. This approach is further complemented by our ability to locate buyers through our local community referral network.

LEYTON TEAM  Our multi-lingual team is staffed by professionals in a range of fields... from sales, to marketing, auctioneering, property management and administration both Residential and Commercial. This gives us the ability to provide enhanced cultural understanding to our clients. The result is less ambiguity in the sales and leasing process and more satisfied clients who feel more informed and in control.

LOCAL EXPERTISE Our intimate knowledge of the local property market is unsurpassed, enabling us to provide the highest quality advise and insight, our strong focus and customised approach to client service that sets us apart. Our team is well informed, professional and dedicated.  We are passionate about Real Estate and whole-heartedly love what we do!

TRANSPARENCY  We place a premium on transparency and clarity. We share information and develop business relationships built on trust.  Our ethical approach and our professional standards has been the foundation of Leyton's business growth. It has allowed us to be recognised as one of the most reputable and trusted agencies in the local community. We are confident that we can meet your property needs and we welcome the opportunity to work with you in the future.

COMMUNITY FOCUS

Finally, we believe in supporting our local community and continue to invest in Springvale Snow Fest, Local sporting bodies and the Royal Children's Hospital. We love Real Estate and we're passionate about our community. It’s just one way we can help to make a difference.
name: Leyton Real Estate

description:
PAUL JONES REALTY was established in 1984 under the leadership of Paul Vazirianis, who had a vision in creating an Estate Agency that, would provide the upmost professionalism in real estate sales and property management, specialising and servicing the South Eastern suburbs of Melbourne and beyond.

Our office is strategically located on the busy corner of Springvale Road and Union Grove Springvale and provides our clients the highest exposure to show case their properties.

As an independent and boutique real estate agency, we are able to provide a service that is far superior to our competitors, with our management team personally handling the sale and management of your property.

Our mission is to set the highest standard of excellence and to exceed our client’s expectations with excellent service and integrity. Throughout the entire process, we are committed to making the sale and the management of your property an easy and rewarding experience.

Our dedicated and knowledgeable sales, management and administration team and our distinctive brand, enables us to offer a first class range of services to our clients, who prefer to deal with an agency offering personalised real estate service, rather than dealing with a large chain real estate office.

Our specialist approach in marketing properties has resulted in thousands of satisfied customers. We allow time and energy to be spent on a personalised campaign that is individually designed for each property. This ensures maximum, dedicated service to our vendors, which helps ensure that the right buyer is found for each individual property.

Our people are highly reputable, well trained and dedicated to achieving outstanding results. Our Property Management, Sales and Administrative staff is equally committed to achieving outstanding results for our clients

We are totally committed to making every step of the process a positive and pleasant experience whilst working to ensure that the best possible result is achieved for you - the Vendor. 

As a member of the Real Estate Institute of Victoria, we're committed to a strict code of Conduct and Rules of Professional Practice. Our REIV membership means an ethical and professional approach to business and a sense of community spirit.

Appointing Paul Jones Realty and experience a highly professional organisation in action, focused on achieving the best possible result for our clients.
name: Paul Jones Realty

description:
Who is Nicholls Gledhill?

Nicholls Gledhill is the longest operating agency in Endeavour Hills. It is not part of another franchise chain but an independent owner-operated family business managed by Harry Nicholls who started the company himself 40 years ago.

Harry is also a Certified Practising Valuer (AAPI), the only one in Endeavour Hills, an associate of the Real estate Institute of Victoria (AREI) and a past president of the REIV (Waverley Branch).

Other staff includes Harry’s son Matthew Nicholls (Office Manager) Laurel Heath (Rental Property Manager) who has had years of experience in this specialised field of real estate plus our dedicated team of sales, reception and clerical staff.

The fact that we operate from our own premises within the Terrace Shopping Centre means that we do not have the substantial overheads experienced by our competitors, expenses such as franchise fees, high shopping centre rentals, group advertising levies etc. Consequently we can offer a more experienced and professional service at more competitive rates.

In order to further improve our service to clients we have just taken over the adjacent premises and have totally refurbished our newly enlarged office complex.

As a result we can now boast the most impressive modern real estate office in the district as well as the biggest and best window display which is kept right up to date with all the best and latest listings. This display works day and night, week-in, week-out attracting potential buyers seeking home in the area. Undoubtedly the best possible place to present your home to the market.
name: Nicholls Gledhill

description:
The #1 Endeavour Hills Real Estate Agents

The last twelve months have been an exciting time for us. We have successfully taken the number one spot for real estate agents in Endeavour Hills by a wide margin, working hard for our vendors to achieve the very best possible prices. With convenient access to the city and major shopping centres, as well as beautiful walking tracks and parkland, this area is a fantastic location for people looking to buy. This is one of the reasons why we have been so successful in helping many satisfied vendors in finding the best price.

Why we’re number one
Here at O’Brien Real Estate Endeavour Hills, we ensure to take care of each and every one of our vendors. Our team of qualified and enthusiastic agents will go above and beyond to achieve the best possible sales result every time, no exceptions. Our sole concern is the outcome we accomplish for our clients, because at the end of the day a business such as this is primarily based on our past successes and the testimonials of our previous clients.

As this is always at the front of our minds, we are able to approach each sales process individually, with the enthusiasm and commitment that you should expect when selling your property. This is just one of the reasons why we have managed to take majority of the market share in just under 12 months, currently residing at a commanding 31%. Another contributing factor is our dedicated team, which is fortunate enough to have the leading agents in the Endeavour Hills area, vendors can rest assured that we’ll get them the best prices, every time.

Property Rental Management Services
Further to our leading sales agents, we provide an extensive and professional team of rental property managers, to remove any and all stresses that have a habit of showing up when you decide to buy an investment property and get into the rental market. Our managers have a great deal of experience to safeguard your investment, and ensure you get the rental payments on time.

Talk to us today

To book in an appraisal for your property by one of our estate agents, or if you’d like to have a discussion with a representative from our property management team, please get in touch with us today on (03) 8768 0400. We have specialised teams dealing with suburbs throughout the South East of Melbourne including Berwick, Cranbourne, and Narre Warren just to name a few.
name: OBrien Real Estate Endeavour Hills

description:
As the name implies, at Berwick Estate Agents, we're locals. We love our community and have a deep understanding of our local property market. With a combined real estate experience of 60 years, the team at Berwick Estate Agents, owned and operated by John Sprakel, takes the time to understand what it is you need and then partners with you to provide a tailored service that caters to your unique circumstances. Whether you're looking to buy or sell, rent or lease, upgrade or downsize, invest or occupy the team at Berwick Estate Agents have the expertise to ensure the entire experience is hassle free and gets you the best result at the best price.


Our team specialises in properties found in Berwick, Beaconsfield, Narre Warren, Narre Warren South, Narre Warren North, Clyde North, Clyde, Cranbourne North, Cranbourne, Hallam, Endeavour Hills Officer and Pakenham. Experts in all areas of real estate Whether you're a first time buyer or an experienced investor, looking for the perfect rental property or the right tenants, downsizing or looking for the right home to raise a family, at Berwick Estate Agebnts we can help you take that next step. Take a few moments to meet our team of experienced real estate professionals, then give us a call on 03 9796 2666 to discuss how we can help you realise your property dreams.

description:
Hall & Partners can trace its origins back to 1917 when Frank Facey commenced trading in Dandenong. In 1956 the company moved to its current office in busy Lonsdale Street.

In 1982 we joined the First National Real Estate group, which gave us the strength and support of 600 offices throughout  Australia and New Zealand.

Michael Hall purchased the Dandenong Office from the Facey family in 1990 and his son Leigh, along with Nicole Knecht are partners in the firm, all of whom are actively involved in the day to day running of the business. 

Whilst being proud of our history it was decided in 2005 to move our emphasis to the future, consequently we changed our name to Hall & Partners First National, which reflects the true ownership of the company.

Our team of experienced professionals are well established in the area and provide the highest level of service to the local community which includes listing properties on multiple web sites, a local property magazine and marketing via our inhouse marketing department.
name: Hall & Partners First National Dandenong

description:
An office with a long history in one area is an office with extensive local knowledge, market know-how and a long history of success.  

Stockdale & Leggo Dandenong – widely regarded as the local agency of choice for sales results, auction success, and professional property management – was established in the early 1970s.

It has also since evolved with the changing area, buyer demographics, and the ever-changing property industry to remain at the forefront of innovative, cutting-edge real estate service provision and results.  

The award-winning office is well known as the local auction specialist – for both auction numbers and success rates – throughout Dandenong, Endeavour Hills, Hallam, Doveton, Noble Park, Keysborough and surrounds. The team has conducted some 100 auctions per year for the last 20 years, well outstripping numbers conducted by others in the area. More importantly, their clearance rate exceeds 90%, which is significantly higher than the industry average.

The office – comprising a large, expert team of multi-lingual professionals – enjoys a strong reputation, loyal base of repeat and referral clients, and positive working relationships with its valued clients. “We work within a culture of success that goes back some 40 years,” says Neil. “Putting in 100% - whether we’re invited into someone’s home to conduct an appraisal or screening for the best tenants for our landlords – is the only way we know.”  

 The office is a multiple recipient of the prestigious Stockdale & Leggo Gold Achievement Award for its consistently high levels of professional excellence and results. It is also consistently positioned as one of the top performing offices in the entire Stockdale & Leggo network.
name: Stockdale & Leggo Dandenong

description:
Our company had its beginning in 1917.  The founder father,  Frank Facey was born in Cranbourne, Victoria and after a career in coach building , started  a Real Estate business in Dandenong.

Frank opened the doors of his Estate Agency in the main street of Dandenong and in 1945 a new site was purchased and a new office built.  In fact, today the current  First National Real Estate Hall & Partners  office is on the same site.

Frank’s son Angus joined his father in the business in 1930.  His son Andrew followed in his footsteps and joined his father in the business in 1968 and took over the management in 1974 .

During the 90’s the group comprised an industrial office in Dandenong as well as residential offices in Dandenong, Berwick, Narre Warren, Endeavour Hills , Mulgrave, Glen Waverley and Pakenham.

The Berwick office combined with Hudson Real Estate Berwick in the late  90’s and in 2002 combined with Cremin Real Estate (Pakenham) .  Both Bill Hudson and Jack Cremin were icons in their  communities.  In recent years the group has consolidated to 3 offices located in  Berwick, Narre Warren  & Pakenham.

Exciting times at First National.  In  July 2011 another change to the business with Andrew Facey our friend and landlord  selling out  and reserving the name Frank Facey for his new development  company.  Our new trading name will be First National Real Estate Neilson Partners with the partnership  across our 3 offices, Narre Warren, Berwick and Pakenham.

Modern technology has been embraced with the computer support linking all residential offices to promote all properties and to support our vendors.  As members of First National we also enjoy the benefit of a 500-office strong referral network throughout Australia and New Zealand.

Today we offer property management across our 3 offices, both residential and commercial as well as sales of all categories of real estate.

Our commitment is long term and to fulfil that our aim is to provide the best in service and results.
name: First National Real Estate Neilson Partners Narre Warren
